1
00:02:52,375 --> 00:02:53,442
早上好
Good morning.

2
00:02:53,443 --> 00:02:55,411
现在是美丽的库母茨郡的上午八点
It's 8:00 in wonderful Coombs County,

3
00:02:55,412 --> 00:02:58,714
本地警方再一次拒绝确认或否认…
where once again state police have refused to confirm or deny

4
00:02:58,715 --> 00:03:02,318
当地居民接连目睹的神秘“空中之光”的发现
more of those mysterious "lights in the sky" sightings by local residents.

5
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:04,787
以下是“漫游空中”电台记者对目击者…
Roving air reporters spoke with Miss Josie Floss,

6
00:03:04,788 --> 00:03:06,255
乔西福洛斯女士所作的采访
who made just such a sighting.

7
00:03:06,256 --> 00:03:08,891
我亲眼看见那些亮光
I've seen those lights with my own eyes.

8
00:03:08,892 --> 00:03:12,191
当我报警的时候，他们告诉我说那是沼气在燃烧
And when I called the police, they told me it was swamp gas.

9
00:03:13,997 --> 00:03:17,232
简直是扯淡！库母茨郡哪儿来的沼气？
Bullshit! Ain't no swamps in Coombs County!

10
00:03:17,233 --> 00:03:19,368
我跟你说，非法的外来生物将借助这光…
I tell you, with them illegal aliens...

11
00:03:19,369 --> 00:03:21,838
又是个好天气啊！
Gonna be a sparkling day.

12
00:03:22,806 --> 00:03:24,306
好天气！
Sparkling.

13
00:03:24,307 --> 00:03:28,267
简直要把我逼疯了！克莱拉！
Makes me crazy! Clara!

14
00:03:29,145 --> 00:03:30,746
克莱拉！
Clara!

15
00:03:30,747 --> 00:03:33,082
我这儿又没电了，克莱拉！
My electric's gone out again, Clara!

16
00:03:33,083 --> 00:03:34,617
我要错过我的肥皂剧了！
I'm gonna miss my soaps!

17
00:03:34,618 --> 00:03:35,718
行了，你别嚷嚷了！
Oh, stop your yakking.

18
00:03:35,719 --> 00:03:36,852
比尔？
Bill?

19
00:03:36,853 --> 00:03:39,355
比尔，艾尔维拉那儿又停电了
Bill, Elvira's blacked out again.

20
00:03:39,356 --> 00:03:40,623
帮我传个话
Pass the word.

21
00:03:40,624 --> 00:03:41,824
过得愉快，宝贝儿！
Have a nice day, honey.

22
00:03:41,825 --> 00:03:43,292
好的。谢谢你，布恩夫人。你也一样
Okay, thanks, Mrs. Boone. You, too.

23
00:03:44,094 --> 00:03:46,228
艾尔维拉那儿又没电了
Elvira's got no electric.

24
00:03:46,229 --> 00:03:49,531
她看不成她的肥皂剧了。她要气炸了！
She can't see her soaps, she'll hyperventilate.

25
00:03:49,532 --> 00:03:50,933
是个野餐的好日子，玛姬！
Great day for a picnic, Maggie!

26
00:03:50,934 --> 00:03:53,002
我真是等不及了，布恩先生。祝你逮到条大鱼哦！
Can't wait, Mr. Boone. Catch yourself a big one!

27
00:03:53,003 --> 00:03:54,069
尽力而为
If I can!

28
00:03:54,070 --> 00:03:56,839
奶奶，你的午餐做好放在冰箱里了
Granny, I fixed your lunch and put it in the fridge.

29
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:57,973
玩得尽兴哦，孩子！
Have fun, child.

30
00:03:57,974 --> 00:03:59,141
你确定你一个人能行吗？
Sure you're gonna be okay?

31
00:03:59,142 --> 00:04:00,209
我没事的，宝贝儿
I'll be fine, dear.

32
00:04:00,210 --> 00:04:02,406
你管你去吧。再见！
Now you just run along. Bye!

33
00:04:07,617 --> 00:04:08,817
嗨，罗根夫人
Hi, Mrs. Rogan.

34
00:04:08,818 --> 00:04:09,952
嗨，玛姬
Hi, Maggie.

35
00:04:09,953 --> 00:04:12,221
野餐盒找到了吗？
Did you find that picnic basket yet?

36
00:04:12,222 --> 00:04:13,288
在客厅里呢
It's in the living room.

37
00:04:13,289 --> 00:04:15,324
哦，谢谢。亚里克斯呢？
Oh, thanks. Where's Alex?

38
00:04:15,325 --> 00:04:16,692
他还能去哪儿呢？
Where else?

39
00:04:16,693 --> 00:04:17,922
对了
Right.

40
00:04:19,229 --> 00:04:20,526
路易斯
Louis.

41
00:04:23,733 --> 00:04:25,134
早上好，太空之子路易斯
Good morning, space-son Louis.

42
00:04:25,135 --> 00:04:26,468
地球人啊！
Earthling.

43
00:04:26,469 --> 00:04:27,800
路易斯
Louis!

44
00:04:27,937 --> 00:04:29,269
珍妮！
Jane!

45
00:04:29,839 --> 00:04:32,307
艾尔维拉那儿又没电了
Elvira's electric is out again,

46
00:04:32,308 --> 00:04:35,642
她要是看不到她的肥皂剧又要发疯了！
and she's gonna get hyper if she can't see her soaps!

47
00:04:36,713 --> 00:04:39,348
奶奶，告诉艾尔维拉，亚里克斯会赶在肥皂剧开始前…
Granny, tell Elvira that Alex will be over

48
00:04:39,349 --> 00:04:41,917
把线路修好的
to patch her electric in time for the soaps.

49
00:04:41,918 --> 00:04:44,353
我会告诉她的，珍妮。艾尔维拉！
I'll tell her, Jane. Elvira!

50
00:04:44,354 --> 00:04:45,888
-路易斯！ -艾尔维拉！
- Louis! - Elvira!

51
00:04:45,889 --> 00:04:47,489
路易斯！
Louis!

52
00:04:47,490 --> 00:04:49,024
去把亚里克斯叫过来
Go tell Alex that I need him.

53
00:04:49,025 --> 00:04:50,526
当心着点，外星人！
Beware, aliens.

54
00:04:50,527 --> 00:04:52,723
路易斯 罗根――宇宙军学员…
Louis Rogan, the cosmic cadet,

55
00:04:52,862 --> 00:04:55,058
太空复仇者――前来收拾你！
the space avenger, is on your case.

56
00:04:59,702 --> 00:05:01,470
你好，星空战士！
Greetings, Starfighter!

57
00:05:01,471 --> 00:05:04,840
你已被星空联盟录取，誓死保卫边境
You have been recruited by the Star League to defend the Frontier

58
00:05:04,841 --> 00:05:07,509
抗击约和柯-旦舰队的入侵
against Yur and the Ko-Dan Armada.

59
00:05:07,510 --> 00:05:09,604
作好准备！即将发射升空！
Get ready. Prepare for blastoff!

60
00:05:14,284 --> 00:05:15,517
好了，开始吧！
Okay. Let's go.

61
00:05:15,518 --> 00:05:18,613
准备进行目标射击训练，星空战士！
Prepare for target light practice, Starfighter.

62
00:05:20,256 --> 00:05:22,350
亚里克斯，妈妈在找你！
Mom's looking for you, Alex.

63
00:05:29,432 --> 00:05:31,457
打那儿！打那儿！
Right there! Right there!

64
00:05:35,739 --> 00:05:37,272
瞄准
Aim.

65
00:05:37,273 --> 00:05:38,373
等他们经过中点时…
They're all through the center.

66
00:05:38,374 --> 00:05:39,808
就射击，知道了吗？
Shoot them, okay?

67
00:05:39,809 --> 00:05:41,877
现在自下向上射击
Now from the bottom up, okay.

68
00:05:41,878 --> 00:05:43,612
那里有一个
There's one right over there.

69
00:05:43,613 --> 00:05:45,614
行，打得不错。那里！
Okay, doing good. Right up there.

70
00:05:45,615 --> 00:05:46,782
把你的头挪开好吧，路易斯？
Move your head, will you, Louis?

71
00:05:46,783 --> 00:05:47,841
啊，对不起
Uh, sorry.

72
00:05:52,055 --> 00:05:53,689
玛姬！
Maggie!

73
00:05:53,690 --> 00:05:57,023
嘿，大伙儿！你们好吗？
Hey, you guys. Hi. How you doing?

74
00:05:59,362 --> 00:06:01,730
快点儿，亚里克斯。他们到了！
Come on, Alex. They're here!

75
00:06:01,731 --> 00:06:04,166
玛姬――拖车场女王！
Maggie, queen of the trailer park!

76
00:06:05,969 --> 00:06:08,770
星空战士亚里克斯 罗根请求…
Well, Starfighter Alex Rogan requests permission

77
00:06:08,771 --> 00:06:11,540
转由我弟弟路易斯来驾驶，长官！
to turn the bridge over to my little brother, Louis, sir!

78
00:06:11,541 --> 00:06:14,476
哈哈，你们这群白痴死定了！
Okay, you dorks are dead.

79
00:06:16,279 --> 00:06:18,447
你被打败了。请再投入二十五美分
You are defeated. 25 cents more, please.

80
00:06:18,448 --> 00:06:20,048
哦，破玩意儿！
Oh, crapola.

81
00:06:20,049 --> 00:06:22,151
-罗根，快点儿！ -嘿，亚里克斯，日子过得可好？
- Rogan, come on. - Hey, Alex, how you doing, man?

82
00:06:22,152 --> 00:06:24,286
-稍等一下 -我们快走吧，伙计
- Just a second. - Big Al. Let's do it, buddy!

83
00:06:24,287 --> 00:06:25,880
你在干什么？
What are you doing?

84
00:06:26,022 --> 00:06:27,615
快啊，亚里克斯。赶紧！
Come on, Alex. Hurry up!

85
00:06:30,326 --> 00:06:31,860
亚里克斯，你到底去不去？
Alex, did it come yet?

86
00:06:31,861 --> 00:06:34,530
噢，不。我不想去了
Uh, no. I don't think so.

87
00:06:34,531 --> 00:06:35,798
这次又怎么了，罗根？
What's it this time, Rogan?

88
00:06:35,799 --> 00:06:37,266
你要打算参军了？
You joining the Foreign Legion?

89
00:06:37,667 --> 00:06:38,901
是，长官，乡亲们。都来看看啊！
Yes, sir, folks. Step right up.

90
00:06:38,902 --> 00:06:40,302
见见我们的冒险家亚里克斯 罗根的…
Meet boy adventurer Alex Rogan

91
00:06:40,303 --> 00:06:43,398
走向失败的世界环游
on the last leg of his worldwide tour to nowhere.

92
00:06:45,341 --> 00:06:46,832
很好笑哦，布雷克
Funny, Blake.

93
00:06:47,477 --> 00:06:50,379
你们以为我在这儿就是看你们显摆汽车…
You guys think I'm gonna hang out here, watch you shine your pickup,

94
00:06:50,380 --> 00:06:54,339
每个星期六晚上在酒店喝得烂醉，还吐得一塌糊涂…
go to the drive-in, get drunk and throw up every Saturday night,

95
00:06:55,318 --> 00:06:57,452
还跟在别人屁股后面上大学？
go to City College like everybody else?

96
00:06:57,453 --> 00:06:59,922
得了吧，伙计。我要用生命成就一番大业
Forget it, man. I'm doing something with my life.

97
00:06:59,923 --> 00:07:02,491
-哦！较真儿先生！ -亚里克斯！
- Mr. Serioso. - Alex!

98
00:07:02,492 --> 00:07:03,992
什么事？
Yeah?

99
00:07:03,993 --> 00:07:06,155
宝贝儿，艾尔维拉家又停电了
Honey, Elvira's electric is out.

100
00:07:07,430 --> 00:07:09,498
哦，妈，那要花掉我一整天
Oh, Ma, that's gonna take all day.

101
00:07:09,499 --> 00:07:11,466
我还打算去银湖玩呢
I was going to Silver Lake.

102
00:07:11,467 --> 00:07:15,070
宝贝儿，我知道。真的很抱歉。我要做中饭和晚饭
Honey, I know. I'm sorry. I'm working lunch and dinner.

103
00:07:15,071 --> 00:07:17,301
我一天都要在镇上
I'm gonna be in town all day!

104
00:07:19,542 --> 00:07:22,068
哦，好吧。算了，妈，我去修吧
Oh, all right. Okay, Ma. I'll do it.

105
00:07:22,645 --> 00:07:24,170
谢谢你了，宝贝儿！
Thanks, honey.

106
00:07:26,416 --> 00:07:28,179
我们要迟到了
We're gonna be late.

107
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:32,520
那…你们…
Look. You...

108
00:07:32,655 --> 00:07:34,122
你们去吧。我不去了
You'd just better go ahead without me.

109
00:07:34,123 --> 00:07:35,691
不，亚里克斯，我留下
No. Alex, I'll stay.

110
00:07:35,692 --> 00:07:37,717
不用，没关系的。修好得要花上一段时间
No. That's okay. This'll take a while.

111
00:07:37,860 --> 00:07:39,886
我修好了来找你们
I'll catch up with you later.

112
00:07:40,830 --> 00:07:42,064
亚里克斯…
Alex...

113
00:07:49,272 --> 00:07:50,672
拜拜，罗根！
Bye-bye, Rogan!

114
00:07:50,673 --> 00:07:51,970
等会儿见啦，老兄！
See you, dude!

115
00:07:56,045 --> 00:07:58,412
亚里克斯，快来帮忙啊！
Alex, come help me!

116
00:07:59,949 --> 00:08:02,782
嘿，亚里克斯，能帮我一下吗？
Hey, Alex. Could you give me a hand here?

117
00:08:06,689 --> 00:08:08,419
谢谢啦，亚里克斯！
Thanks, Alex!

118
00:08:28,278 --> 00:08:30,303
我们今晚该做点什么呢？
What should we do tonight?

119
00:08:30,980 --> 00:08:32,914
谁知道啊
I don't know.

120
00:08:33,049 --> 00:08:35,050
打牌怎么样？
How about cards?

121
00:08:35,051 --> 00:08:36,883
嘿，是个好主意！
Hey, that's a good idea.

122
00:08:37,020 --> 00:08:38,851
但是我们昨晚刚打过啊
But we played cards last night.

123
00:08:39,956 --> 00:08:41,185
那…
Well...

124
00:08:42,358 --> 00:08:45,260
太太们今晚要进城跳舞
The missus wants to go into town tonight and go dancing.

125
00:09:16,259 --> 00:09:19,592
鱼在水里使老大劲地向下扯
The fish were really biting down there at the stream.

126
00:09:20,363 --> 00:09:23,094
今天钓得真尽兴
It was pleasant fishing today.

127
00:09:23,833 --> 00:09:26,825
是啊。明天依然是个好天气
Yup. It's gonna be pleasant tomorrow, too.

128
00:09:28,438 --> 00:09:32,033
根据农历来看，今年夏天可是个好夏天啊
Gonna be a pleasant summer according to Farmer's Almanac.

129
00:09:32,375 --> 00:09:34,366
是啊。我最爱农历了
Yeah. I love the Farmer's Almanac.

130
00:09:34,510 --> 00:09:36,501
我研究了好多年了
I've been reading it for years.

131
00:09:38,614 --> 00:09:40,282
你好，星空战士！
Greetings, Starfighter.

132
00:09:40,283 --> 00:09:42,513
你已被星空联盟录取，誓死保卫边境
You have been recruited by the Star League

133
00:09:42,885 --> 00:09:46,219
抗击约和柯-旦舰队的入侵
to defend the Frontier against Yur and the Ko-Dan Armada.

134
00:09:46,422 --> 00:09:48,090
是啊，是啊
Yeah. Yeah.

135
00:09:48,091 --> 00:09:50,457
作好准备！即将发射升空！
Get ready. Prepare for blastoff.

136
00:09:56,232 --> 00:09:59,327
准备进行目标射击训练，星空战士！
Prepare for target light practice, Starfighter.

137
00:10:09,045 --> 00:10:10,345
哦，嗨，亚里克斯
Oh, hi, Alex.

138
00:10:10,346 --> 00:10:11,541
嘿，Otis
Hey, Otis.

139
00:10:15,651 --> 00:10:17,449
你的玛姬呢？
Where's your Maggie?

140
00:10:18,855 --> 00:10:20,455
问得好
Good question.

141
00:10:20,456 --> 00:10:21,947
我想…在外面玩得尽兴着呢
Out having a good time, I guess.

142
00:10:22,825 --> 00:10:26,194
哦，你从来也没玩得尽兴过
Oh. And you never have a good time.

143
00:10:26,195 --> 00:10:27,562
对不对？
Is that it?

144
00:10:27,563 --> 00:10:30,565
是啊。我就喜欢帮人维修用了三十年的保险丝箱
Oh, sure. I love patching 30-year-old fuse panels

145
00:10:30,566 --> 00:10:32,796
还喜欢帮人通马桶
and plunging people's toilets.

146
00:10:33,569 --> 00:10:34,970
Otis，我从来也没有机会…
Otis, I never even get a chance

147
00:10:34,971 --> 00:10:36,530
在这儿玩得尽兴过
to have a good time around here.

148
00:10:38,274 --> 00:10:41,801
事情总是会改变的。永远都这样
Things change. Always do.

149
00:10:45,181 --> 00:10:47,249
你会有机会的
You'll get your chance.

150
00:10:47,250 --> 00:10:49,551
重要的是，当它来临时…
lmportant thing is, when it comes,

151
00:10:49,552 --> 00:10:53,284
你要用双手紧紧地抓住它
you got to grab it with both hands and hold on tight.

152
00:10:57,360 --> 00:11:00,523
敌军在三、六、七区，快速接近中
Enemy squadrons in Sectors 3, 6, 7 closing fast.

153
00:11:09,939 --> 00:11:11,106
谢谢你，杰克
Thanks, Jack.

154
00:11:11,107 --> 00:11:12,207
别客气
You're welcome.

155
00:11:12,208 --> 00:11:13,607
-晚安，玛姬 -晚安
Good night, Maggie. Good night.

156
00:11:47,410 --> 00:11:49,478
我还以为你会去湖边找我呢
Thought you were gonna meet me at the lake.

157
00:11:49,479 --> 00:11:50,946
发生了什么事？
What happened?

158
00:11:51,514 --> 00:11:53,505
相同的事总是发生。我没办法脱身
Same thing that always happens. I couldn't get away.

159
00:11:57,019 --> 00:11:58,578
其他人呢？
Where's everybody else?

160
00:11:58,721 --> 00:12:00,280
哦，他们去看电影了
Oh, they went to a movie.

161
00:12:03,025 --> 00:12:06,128
老杰克 布雷克碰巧和你同路，啊？
Old Jack Blake just happened to be going your way, huh?

162
00:12:06,129 --> 00:12:08,256
敌军在三区出现
Enemy squadron in Sector 3.

163
00:12:10,099 --> 00:12:12,200
他说他正好顺路回家
He said it was on his way home.

164
00:12:12,201 --> 00:12:14,363
布雷克住在镇的那头
Blake lives on the other side of town.

165
00:12:14,637 --> 00:12:16,401
拜托，亚里克斯
Come on, Alex.

166
00:12:17,573 --> 00:12:19,735
我就想回到你身边
I wanted to get back to you.

167
00:12:22,378 --> 00:12:23,812
可以了吧？
Okay?

168
00:12:29,085 --> 00:12:31,645
打得不错，星空战士！你真行！
Good show, Starfighter! Way to go.

169
00:12:32,822 --> 00:12:34,312
亚里克斯，看啊！
Alex, look!

170
00:12:35,324 --> 00:12:38,123
哦，天啊！有多少？九十万？
Oh, my God. What is that? 900,000!

171
00:12:43,399 --> 00:12:48,166
九十万！你要破纪录了！
900,000! You gonna bust the record!

172
00:12:50,273 --> 00:12:54,976
嘿！嘿！大家，听好了！
Hey! Hey! Listen up, everybody!

173
00:12:54,977 --> 00:12:57,571
亚里克斯破纪录了！
Alex is going for the record!

174
00:12:58,714 --> 00:13:00,114
纪录？
Record?

175
00:13:00,249 --> 00:13:01,750
去…去看看
Take... Take a hand.

176
00:13:01,751 --> 00:13:04,413
打中了！哦，他就要打中那架了！
Got them! Oh, he's gonna get that one!

177
00:13:08,457 --> 00:13:09,948
你行的！
You can do it!

178
00:13:10,927 --> 00:13:12,227
Otis？
Otis?

179
00:13:14,697 --> 00:13:17,365
Otis，你在嚷嚷什么？发生什么事了？
Otis, what are you yelling about? What's wrong?

180
00:13:17,366 --> 00:13:19,534
快来啊！快！
Come on! Come on!

181
00:13:19,535 --> 00:13:21,469
他就要破纪录了！
He's going to bust the record!

182
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:24,506
快！快！
Hurry! Hurry!

183
00:13:24,507 --> 00:13:26,808
大家都退后！别挤到他！
Everyone get back! Don't crowd him!

184
00:13:26,809 --> 00:13:28,834
我说了，快退后！
I said, get back!

185
00:13:37,286 --> 00:13:39,654
亚里克斯，你以前从来没打出过这个成绩！
Alex, you never got this far before!

186
00:13:39,655 --> 00:13:41,021
加油，亚里克斯！
Go, Alex!

187
00:13:46,862 --> 00:13:48,228
真争气！
Good boy!

188
00:13:50,166 --> 00:13:52,901
柯-旦指挥舰进入射程
Ko-Dan command ship entering kill zone.

189
00:13:52,902 --> 00:13:54,102
指挥舰！
Command ship!

190
00:13:54,103 --> 00:13:55,370
哦，是指挥舰！
Oh, command ship!

191
00:13:55,371 --> 00:13:57,005
指挥舰是什么？
What's a command ship?

192
00:13:57,006 --> 00:13:58,974
你行的，亚里克斯！你绝对行！
You can do it, Alex! You can do it!

193
00:14:03,379 --> 00:14:06,381
再来一次！加油啊！就是它！
One more now. Come on! That's the one!

194
00:14:06,382 --> 00:14:08,646
要打的就是它！
That's the one we want!

195
00:14:17,560 --> 00:14:19,527
好啊！太棒了！
Yeah! Yeah!

196
00:14:52,161 --> 00:14:54,663
晚安。你真行，亚里克斯！
Good night. Way to go, Alex!

197
00:14:54,664 --> 00:14:55,764
晚安，孩子们
Good night, kids.

198
00:14:55,765 --> 00:14:57,255
亚里克斯，你真够可以的
Alex, you're something else.

199
00:14:57,400 --> 00:14:58,967
你真棒，孩子
You're wonderful, boy.

200
00:14:58,968 --> 00:15:00,663
谢谢
Thank you.

201
00:15:00,803 --> 00:15:02,604
我说的话准能成真
If I said it once, I said it a thousand times.

202
00:15:02,605 --> 00:15:04,205
那孩子见得了世面
That boy's gonna go places.

203
00:15:04,206 --> 00:15:05,765
他真够聪明的
That's one smart boy.

204
00:15:20,256 --> 00:15:21,883
晚安，亚里克斯
Good night, Alex.

205
00:15:24,293 --> 00:15:26,761
“晚安，亚里克斯”？等等
"Good night, Alex"? Wait a second.

206
00:15:26,762 --> 00:15:28,924
玛姬？玛姬？
Maggie? Maggie?

207
00:15:30,766 --> 00:15:33,360
等一下。你要去哪里？
Hold on a second. Where are you going?

208
00:15:38,140 --> 00:15:39,665
怎么了？
What's wrong?

209
00:15:40,943 --> 00:15:44,038
我突然才发觉…
Well, I guess it just hit me.

210
00:15:44,747 --> 00:15:47,248
你真的要离开这儿了，对吗？
You really are leaving here, aren't you?

211
00:15:47,249 --> 00:15:49,451
当然，我当然要走。我们一起离开这里
Of course, I'm leaving. We're both gonna leave here.

212
00:15:49,452 --> 00:15:51,986
-我们一起，亚里克斯？ -是啊
Both of us, Alex? Yeah.

213
00:15:51,987 --> 00:15:54,322
我们对此已经谈过了
We talked about this.

214
00:15:54,323 --> 00:15:55,824
等我入了学，我就会找个地方…
When I get to school, I'm gonna find a place

215
00:15:55,825 --> 00:15:57,292
然后回来接你
and I'm gonna come back and get you.

216
00:15:57,293 --> 00:15:58,817
那…奶奶怎么办？
Well, what about Granny?

217
00:15:59,762 --> 00:16:01,093
奶奶？
Granny?

218
00:16:03,499 --> 00:16:05,500
其实是你自己害怕离开这个拖车场吧？
Truth is, you're scared of leaving this trailer park.

219
00:16:05,501 --> 00:16:08,002
我才不怕离开这个拖车场呢，亚里克斯
I'm not scared of leaving this trailer park, Alex.

220
00:16:08,003 --> 00:16:10,063
嘿，听好
Hey. Listen.

221
00:16:12,775 --> 00:16:16,370
无论发生什么，我都和你在一起，对吧？
Whatever happens, it's you and me forever, right?

222
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,275
对吧？
Right?

223
00:16:21,917 --> 00:16:23,943
我真的很爱你，亚里克斯
I love you so much, Alex.

224
00:16:24,086 --> 00:16:26,111
我也永远爱你，玛姬
I'll always love you, Maggs.

225
00:16:30,259 --> 00:16:32,091
真恶心
Diarrhea.

226
00:16:47,710 --> 00:16:50,907
玛姬！玛姬！
Maggie! Maggie!

227
00:16:51,614 --> 00:16:55,416
亚里克斯，我要回去了。晚安
Alex, I got to go in. Good night.

228
00:16:55,418 --> 00:16:57,352
-晚安 -晚安
Good night. Good night.

229
00:17:16,605 --> 00:17:20,167
总有一天他们会说：“一切就是从这开始的”
Someday they're gonna say, "This is where it all began."

230
00:17:20,843 --> 00:17:21,943
什么意思？
What?

231
00:17:21,944 --> 00:17:24,242
妈，我终于打破了“星空战士”的纪录
Mom, I finally broke the Starfighter record.

232
00:17:24,780 --> 00:17:27,340
哦，那太好了，宝贝儿
Oh, that's nice, dear.

233
00:17:27,483 --> 00:17:30,118
好？简直是令人惊叹！
Nice? It's stupendous!

234
00:17:30,119 --> 00:17:32,453
亚里克斯
Uh, Alex,

235
00:17:32,454 --> 00:17:35,523
布兰纳先生知道你想尽快看到这个…
Mr. Brenner knew that you'd want to see this as soon as possible,

236
00:17:35,524 --> 00:17:38,226
所以他把这个带到了餐馆…
so he brought it by the diner and...

237
00:17:38,227 --> 00:17:40,862
我很兴奋，所以就把它打开了
Well, I was so excited, I opened it.

238
00:17:40,863 --> 00:17:42,764
哦，没关系。里面说什么？
Oh, that's okay. What is it?

239
00:17:42,765 --> 00:17:44,562
是关于你的贷款
It's about your loan.

240
00:17:50,239 --> 00:17:53,698
你仍然可以和你的朋友一起上大学
You can still go to City College with your friends.

241
00:18:34,516 --> 00:18:36,451
你好，星空战士！
Greetings, Starfighter.

242
00:18:41,023 --> 00:18:42,123
你好，星空战士！
Greetings, Starfighter.

243
00:18:42,124 --> 00:18:45,026
你已被星空联盟录取，誓死保卫边境
You have been recruited by the Star League to defend the Frontier.

244
00:18:45,027 --> 00:18:46,261
你已被星空联盟录取…
You have been recruited...

245
00:18:46,262 --> 00:18:47,462
你好，星空战士！
Greetings, Starfighter.

246
00:18:47,463 --> 00:18:48,862
你已被星空联盟录取…
You have been recruited...

247
00:18:50,032 --> 00:18:52,023
你已被星空联盟录取…
You have been recruited...

248
00:18:52,401 --> 00:18:54,426
你已被星空联盟录取…
You have been recruited...

249
00:18:56,906 --> 00:18:59,307
作好准备！即将发射升空！
Get ready. Prepare for blastoff.

250
00:19:43,419 --> 00:19:45,717
你好。请问，孩子…
Hello. Excuse me, son.

251
00:19:47,990 --> 00:19:49,657
商店已经关门了，先生
Store's closed, mister.

252
00:19:49,658 --> 00:19:52,393
我不是来买香烟或者泡泡糖的，孩子
I'm not here for cigarettes or bubble gum, my boy.

253
00:19:52,394 --> 00:19:53,395
你能不能告诉我…
Can you tell me the name of the person

254
00:19:53,396 --> 00:19:55,530
打破那边那个游戏纪录的人的名字？
who broke the record on that game over there?

255
00:19:55,531 --> 00:19:57,465
我在哪里可以找到他？
Where I might find him?

256
00:19:59,001 --> 00:20:01,971
是亚里克斯 罗根。他现在就在你面前
Alex Rogan. You're looking at him.

257
00:20:02,671 --> 00:20:05,265
亚里克斯 罗根。啊哈！
Alex Rogan. Aha!

258
00:20:06,041 --> 00:20:08,209
-你是谁？ -森特利是我的名字
Who are you? Centauri's the name.

259
00:20:08,210 --> 00:20:10,611
那个游戏是我发明的。它就是我来这儿的原因
I invented Starfighter, which is why I'm here.

260
00:20:10,612 --> 00:20:12,046
-真的？ -当然
It is? It is.

261
00:20:12,047 --> 00:20:14,682
我们得谈谈一件极重要的事
We have to talk about a matter of utmost importance.

262
00:20:14,683 --> 00:20:16,451
请进入我的办公室
Step into my office.

263
00:20:16,452 --> 00:20:18,852
就是它。进来吧
That's it. Come on now.

264
00:20:19,621 --> 00:20:21,590
没什么好怕的
Nothing to be afraid of.

265
00:20:26,562 --> 00:20:29,361
哦，对了。和我的助手贝塔打个招呼
Oh, yes. Say hello to my assistant, Beta.

266
00:20:30,265 --> 00:20:31,528
你好
Howdy.

267
00:20:33,235 --> 00:20:34,361
嗷！
Ow!

268
00:20:34,703 --> 00:20:37,905
我必须就你的精彩表现恭喜你，我的孩子
I must congratulate you on your virtuoso performance, my boy.

269
00:20:37,906 --> 00:20:39,272
你给森特利留下了深刻的印象
Centauri is impressed.

270
00:20:39,408 --> 00:20:40,875
我见过有人来，也见过有人去…
I've seen them come and I've seen them go.

271
00:20:40,876 --> 00:20:43,077
但是你是最棒的，我的孩子。漂亮！
But you're the best, my boy. Dazzling.

272
00:20:43,078 --> 00:20:45,069
比其他人好十万八千里
Light years ahead of the competition.

273
00:20:45,214 --> 00:20:47,239
这就是为什么森特利要来这儿
Which is why Centauri is here.

274
00:20:47,950 --> 00:20:49,918
他有点事来找你
He's got a little proposition for you.

275
00:20:50,953 --> 00:20:52,182
你有兴趣吗？
Are you interested?

276
00:20:53,522 --> 00:20:54,853
我想是吧
I guess.

277
00:20:56,658 --> 00:20:57,853
嘿！
Hey!

278
00:21:04,299 --> 00:21:05,500
你在干什么？
What are you doing?

279
00:21:05,501 --> 00:21:06,634
听着
Listen.

280
00:21:06,635 --> 00:21:08,469
森特利想要给你一个惊喜
Centauri wants to keep it for a surprise.

281
00:21:08,470 --> 00:21:12,134
相信我，你会喜欢它的。一定会的！
Trust me. Oh, you're gonna love it. Love it!

282
00:21:18,447 --> 00:21:21,883
好笑的是，这一切都是出于一个错误
The amusing thing about this, it's all a big mistake.

283
00:21:21,884 --> 00:21:23,551
那个游戏…
That particular Starfighter game

284
00:21:23,552 --> 00:21:25,553
应该被运往维加斯的
was supposed to be delivered to Vegas,

285
00:21:25,554 --> 00:21:27,722
而不是你们那个在野草和虫子堆里的…
not some flea-speck trailer park

286
00:21:27,723 --> 00:21:29,590
芝麻大小的拖车场
in the middle of tumbleweeds and tarantulas.

287
00:21:29,591 --> 00:21:32,660
所以，一定是宿命，命运――误打误撞地…
So, it must be fate, destiny, blind chance,

288
00:21:32,661 --> 00:21:34,425
甚至可以说是运气――把我们带到一起
luck, even, that brings us together.

289
00:21:35,197 --> 00:21:38,292
有首诗说得好：“往事如烟”
And as the poet says, "The rest is history."

290
00:21:48,610 --> 00:21:51,045
你要去哪儿？为什么要带我去？
Where are you going? Where are you taking me?

291
00:21:51,046 --> 00:21:53,981
我告诉过你了，我要给你一个惊喜
I told you. I wanna save it for a surprise.

292
00:21:53,982 --> 00:21:58,886
嘿，你是不是那种急着先读谜底的孩子？
Hey. Are you the kind of kid who reads the last page of a mystery first?

293
00:21:58,887 --> 00:22:01,355
那些缠着魔术师追问奥秘的孩子？
Who pesters the magician to tell you his tricks?

294
00:22:01,356 --> 00:22:04,025
那些悄悄溜下楼偷看圣诞礼物的孩子？
Who sneaks downstairs to peek at his Christmas presents?

295
00:22:04,026 --> 00:22:06,360
不，你当然不是那样的！
No. Of course you're not!

296
00:22:06,361 --> 00:22:09,160
所以我先不告诉你
That's why I'm not gonna tell you.

297
00:22:10,499 --> 00:22:11,489
哦，天啊
Oh, God.

298
00:22:13,302 --> 00:22:16,601
除此之外，我最喜欢惊喜了。难道你不是吗？
Besides, I just love surprises, don't you?

299
00:22:17,673 --> 00:22:19,197
嘿！看好了！
Hey, look out!

300
00:22:19,575 --> 00:22:20,675
-停车！ -天啊！
Stop! Oh, dear!

301
00:22:20,676 --> 00:22:22,439
快踩刹车！嘿…
Hit the brakes! Hey...

302
00:23:21,703 --> 00:23:24,172
在哥伦比亚星切换为星球驱动模式
Shifting into star drive at Columba Zeta.

303
00:23:24,173 --> 00:23:25,868
抓紧了
Hold tight.

304
00:25:25,894 --> 00:25:29,194
嘿。嘿，让我出去！
Hey. Hey, let me out of here!

305
00:26:11,039 --> 00:26:13,599
应该有一个完全符合逻辑的理由来解释这一切
There's a perfectly logical explanation for all this.

306
00:26:31,626 --> 00:26:33,627
嘿！等等！你要去哪儿？
Hey! Wait! Where you going?

307
00:26:48,343 --> 00:26:51,506
嗨！你好。这是什么？
Hi! How are you? What is this?

308
00:26:52,447 --> 00:26:54,780
听着，你会说英语吗？我…
Listen. Do you speak English? I'd...

309
00:26:55,417 --> 00:26:57,051
这是很不错，可是…
This is nice but...

310
00:27:10,365 --> 00:27:12,133
森特利，这里发生什么情况？
Centauri, what's going on here?

311
00:27:12,134 --> 00:27:14,402
他说你能来这儿他很高兴…
He's just saying how delighted he is that you're here.

312
00:27:14,403 --> 00:27:15,603
还有，如果你有什么需要能让你在这儿过得愉快…
And if there's anything he can do

313
00:27:15,604 --> 00:27:17,605
给他打个电话就行
to make your stay more enjoyable, just give him a ring.

314
00:27:17,606 --> 00:27:20,975
在这儿？你在说些什么？我们在哪儿？
My stay? What are you talking about? Where are we?

315
00:27:20,976 --> 00:27:23,001
欢迎来到赖罗斯星，我的孩子！
Welcome to Rylos, my boy!

316
00:27:24,112 --> 00:27:25,273
赖罗斯？
Rylos?

317
00:27:25,914 --> 00:27:28,315
等等。你的意思是说…就像在游戏里一样？
Wait a minute. You mean... You mean like in a game?

318
00:27:28,316 --> 00:27:30,351
哦，他反应很快嘛。很快，是很快
Oh, he's quick. He's quick. He's very quick.

319
00:27:30,352 --> 00:27:33,554
他瞠目结舌了！再见了，亚里克斯！尽兴哦！
He's speechless. So long, Alex! Have fun!

320
00:27:33,555 --> 00:27:36,957
但愿古鲁七柱的好运永远伴你左右
May the luck of the Seven Pillars of Gulu be with you at all times.

321
00:27:36,958 --> 00:27:40,561
哦，总有一天这些混蛋们会感谢森特利的。相信我吧
Oh, someday these cheapskates will thank Centauri. Trust me.

322
00:27:45,267 --> 00:27:47,167
六月份的到哪儿去了？
Where the hell is June?

323
00:27:52,407 --> 00:27:54,637
犹兰达，小甜心！
Yolanda, baby!

324
00:28:05,387 --> 00:28:06,718
嗨，玛姬
Hi, Maggs.

325
00:28:07,722 --> 00:28:09,088
嗨，路易斯
Hi, Louis.

326
00:28:09,925 --> 00:28:11,125
他起床了吗？
Is he up?

327
00:28:11,126 --> 00:28:15,154
他嘟哝了一个晚上，没睡过
Yeah. He's been up all night moaning.

328
00:28:20,001 --> 00:28:21,333
亚里克斯？
Alex?

329
00:28:25,373 --> 00:28:27,865
你妈妈告诉我贷款的事了
Your mother told me about the loan.

330
00:28:28,443 --> 00:28:30,503
有什么我帮得上的吗？
Is there anything I can do?

331
00:28:37,152 --> 00:28:40,520
听着，如果你需要帮忙，我就在隔壁，好吧？
Listen. I'll be next door if you need anything, okay?

332
00:29:57,332 --> 00:29:58,458
刚星群
Gunstars.

333
00:30:00,569 --> 00:30:02,366
我一定是在做梦
I got to be dreaming.

334
00:30:07,242 --> 00:30:08,342
是啊，没错
Yeah, right.

335
00:30:16,184 --> 00:30:18,619
听着，这里有个大错
Listen, there's been a big mistake.

336
00:30:18,620 --> 00:30:20,588
...immediately after situation report.

337
00:30:20,589 --> 00:30:21,755
Navigation...

338
00:30:21,756 --> 00:30:24,191
欢迎来到星空战士指挥部
Welcome to Starfighter Command.

339
00:30:24,192 --> 00:30:25,326
你在说英语了？
You speak English?

340
00:30:25,327 --> 00:30:28,128
不，你听到的是英语。这要多亏了你的翻译装置
No. You hear English, thanks to your translator device.

341
00:30:28,129 --> 00:30:29,797
赶紧，我们时间不多了
Hurry up. We haven't got much time.

342
00:30:29,798 --> 00:30:31,823
部署会议马上要开始了
The briefing begins immediately.

343
00:30:32,367 --> 00:30:34,101
请和其他录取者一同前往
Join the other recruits.

344
00:30:34,102 --> 00:30:35,900
等等！等等！
Wait a minute! Wait a minute!

345
00:30:36,137 --> 00:30:38,105
等等！你说的录取者是什么意思？
Wait a minute! What are you talking about, recruits?

346
00:30:41,343 --> 00:30:43,106
我简直不能相信！
I don't believe this.

347
00:30:46,248 --> 00:30:50,551
注意。请注意！恩德伦大使已经到达
Attention. Attention, please. Ambassador Enduran has arrived

348
00:30:50,552 --> 00:30:53,851
并将立即开始部署星空战士指挥部的人事工作
and will now address Starfighter Command personnel.

349
00:30:56,791 --> 00:31:00,761
众所周知，我们绝望地探寻了很久…
As you all know, we have been on a desperate quest...

350
00:31:00,762 --> 00:31:02,596
抱歉。抱歉
Excuse me. Excuse me.

351
00:31:02,597 --> 00:31:03,797
…找到你们这些星空战士和领航员
...to find Starfighters and navigators.

352
00:31:07,702 --> 00:31:11,229
我…我真应该把你捏得粉碎！
I should... I should crush you to gorun dust!

353
00:31:12,007 --> 00:31:14,875
对不起，我是不小心的…
I'm sorry... It was an accident.

354
00:31:14,876 --> 00:31:16,401
我不是要故意踩你的…
I didn't mean to step on your...

355
00:31:17,212 --> 00:31:18,646
我也不知道叫它什么东西
Whatever that is.

356
00:31:18,647 --> 00:31:19,813
可怕的生物
Hideous creature.

357
00:31:19,814 --> 00:31:21,305
请允许我继续
If I may continue.

358
00:31:22,250 --> 00:31:23,851
我们的军队已经…
Our forces have...

359
00:31:23,852 --> 00:31:25,419
你别惹伯嘉地
You don't trifle with a Bogati.

360
00:31:25,420 --> 00:31:26,920
他们很好战
They love to fight.

361
00:31:26,921 --> 00:31:29,117
所以我们很适合打这场战争
That's why they're perfect for this war.

362
00:31:31,092 --> 00:31:32,192
你是不是说了“战争”？
Did you say "war"?

363
00:31:32,193 --> 00:31:33,294
没错！
But of course!

364
00:31:33,295 --> 00:31:35,596
不然你认为你在这儿干什么？
Why else do you think you're here?

365
00:31:35,597 --> 00:31:37,698
“你已被星空联盟录取，誓死保卫边境”
You were recruited by the Star League to defend...

366
00:31:37,699 --> 00:31:41,465
“抗击约和柯-旦舰队的入侵”
"...to defend the Frontier against Xur and the Ko-Dan Armada."

367
00:31:43,838 --> 00:31:49,376
很久很久以前，我们的祖先建造了这伟大的边境
Eons ago, our ancestors created our great Frontier,

368
00:31:49,377 --> 00:31:51,712
它对敌人来说是一道屏障
a barrier of energy

369
00:31:51,713 --> 00:31:54,876
维持着和平的宇宙体系
encircling the peaceful systems of the universe,

370
00:31:55,583 --> 00:31:59,782
将潜在的灾祸拒于千里之外
and forever shutting out the scourge that lurks beyond.

371
00:32:02,023 --> 00:32:06,660
大伙，由于无耻的背叛…
Fellow Rylans, because of a dark betrayal,

372
00:32:06,661 --> 00:32:08,696
我们的边境即将瓦解
our Frontier will soon collapse.

373
00:32:11,332 --> 00:32:16,537
所以，我们向你们――星空战士以及你们的领航员们――求助…
So we turn to you, Starfighters and your navigators.

374
00:32:16,538 --> 00:32:20,240
代表着星际联盟几十亿的生命
For of all the billions of creatures in the Star League,

375
00:32:20,241 --> 00:32:23,734
只有你们几个才被证明有那…
only you few were found to possess the

376
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:27,007
天赋
gift.

377
00:32:28,550 --> 00:32:31,719
你，还有你…
You, and you alone,

378
00:32:31,720 --> 00:32:35,451
正站在我们与黑暗势力的中间
stand between us and the black terror of the Ko-Dan.

379
00:32:37,759 --> 00:32:39,454
胜利还是灭亡！
Victory or death!

380
00:32:39,594 --> 00:32:41,361
胜利还是灭亡！
Victory or death!

381
00:32:41,362 --> 00:32:44,465
胜利还是灭亡！胜利还是灭亡！
Victory or death! Victory or death!

382
00:32:44,466 --> 00:32:47,368
胜利还是灭亡！胜利还是灭亡！
Victory or death! Victory or death!

383
00:32:47,369 --> 00:32:50,270
胜利还是灭亡！胜利还是灭亡！
Victory or death! Victory or death!

384
00:32:50,271 --> 00:32:53,006
