Victory or death! Victory or death!

385
00:32:53,007 --> 00:32:55,876
胜利还是灭亡！胜利还是灭亡！
Victory or death! Victory or death!

386
00:32:55,877 --> 00:32:58,879
胜利还是灭亡！胜利还是灭亡！
Victory or death! Victory or death!

387
00:32:58,880 --> 00:33:02,043
胜利还是灭亡！胜利还是灭亡！
Victory or death! Victory or death!

388
00:33:02,517 --> 00:33:05,652
现在，星空战士们，在你们的座位底下…
Now, Starfighters, if you will reach underneath your seats,

389
00:33:05,653 --> 00:33:09,112
你们会发现一个装有一只手的包…
you will find a packet which contains one hand...

390
00:33:12,994 --> 00:33:15,964
这里是限制区域，对你们…
This is a restricted area, off-limits to...

391
00:33:18,800 --> 00:33:21,835
真对不起，星空战士
My apologies, Starfighter.

392
00:33:21,836 --> 00:33:25,272
星际导航员兼一等兵听从您指挥，长官！
Star Navigator First Class Grig at your service, sir!

393
00:33:27,809 --> 00:33:31,278
嗨，我是亚里克斯 罗根，我在家里玩这个游戏…
Hi. I'm Alex Rogan. I was playing this game back home,

394
00:33:31,279 --> 00:33:32,479
后来有个人找到我…
and this guy came up to me.

395
00:33:32,480 --> 00:33:34,415
其实他不是个人，他是外星人，对吧？
Only he's not a guy. He's an alien, right?

396
00:33:34,416 --> 00:33:37,217
然后我坐上他的车――只不过那不是辆车――而是艘宇宙飞船
And I get into his car. Only it's not a car. It's a spaceship.

397
00:33:37,218 --> 00:33:40,721
这里面有个大错误
And, there's been a big mistake.

398
00:33:40,722 --> 00:33:42,689
我是不是要这样理解…
Am I to understand you're actually declining

399
00:33:42,690 --> 00:33:45,058
你拒绝做一名光荣的星空战士？
the honor of becoming a Starfighter?

400
00:33:45,059 --> 00:33:46,460
没错
You got it.

401
00:33:46,461 --> 00:33:47,826
太不可思议了！
Extraordinary!

402
00:33:48,830 --> 00:33:52,596
长久以来，所有的生物都梦想成为星空战士
For eons, all creatures have dreamt of being Starfighters.

403
00:33:53,134 --> 00:33:55,169
-你从哪儿来？ -地球
Where you from? Earth.

404
00:33:55,170 --> 00:33:58,439
我们其实和谁都没在打仗，只是互相在打
And we're not at war with anybody, except each other.

405
00:33:58,440 --> 00:34:02,209
地球？地球可不是星际联盟的正式成员啊…
Earth? Earth isn't a formal member of the Star League,

406
00:34:02,210 --> 00:34:04,578
而且只有等到它成熟以后我们才可以接近
and isn't due to be approached until it matures.

407
00:34:04,579 --> 00:34:07,514
这太没规矩了
This is all highly irregular.

408
00:34:07,515 --> 00:34:09,917
告诉我，是谁征用你的？
Tell me. Who recruited you?

409
00:34:09,918 --> 00:34:11,146
森特利
Centauri.

410
00:34:11,886 --> 00:34:13,020
他来了。就是他！
There he is. That's him!

411
00:34:13,021 --> 00:34:15,456
森特利。我也许认识他
Centauri. I might have known.

412
00:34:20,094 --> 00:34:23,826
又在故伎重演了，对吧，森特利？
Up to your old Excalibur tricks again, eh, Centauri?

413
00:34:24,566 --> 00:34:25,933
你就不知道…
Did it ever occur to you that it is against the law

414
00:34:25,934 --> 00:34:29,236
从星际联盟以外的地方征兵是非法的？
to recruit from worlds outside the Star League?

415
00:34:29,237 --> 00:34:31,330
地球也受到了威胁，不是吗？
Earth's in danger, too, isn't it?

416
00:34:31,473 --> 00:34:33,640
不，我可没有动用神剑测试哦
And, no, I did not use the Excalibur test.

417
00:34:33,641 --> 00:34:35,342
只用了一个叫作“电子游戏”的东西
It was called a video game.

418
00:34:35,343 --> 00:34:36,977
那又有什么关系呢？
What's all the brouhaha?

419
00:34:36,978 --> 00:34:39,847
总之，他没有那种天赋
After all, he does have the gift!

420
00:34:39,848 --> 00:34:42,316
这也许会让你很吃惊…
This may come as a bit of a shock to you,

421
00:34:42,317 --> 00:34:44,649
但是，他并不想成为星空战士
but he doesn't want to be a Starfighter.

422
00:34:45,386 --> 00:34:48,589
不想成为一个…你是个懦夫吗？
Doesn't want to be a... Are you a coward?

423
00:34:48,590 --> 00:34:49,656
你疯了吗？
Are you crazy?

424
00:34:49,657 --> 00:34:51,250
你什么都没告诉过我！
You didn't tell me about any of this!

425
00:34:51,960 --> 00:34:54,027
还钱吧，森特利！
Return the money, Centauri!

426
00:34:54,028 --> 00:34:57,364
还钱？你老糊涂了吗？
Return the money? Are you delirious?

427
00:34:57,365 --> 00:34:59,433
你知道我花了多久发明那游戏…
Do you know how long it took to invent the games,

428
00:34:59,434 --> 00:35:00,634
进行推广…
to merchandise them,

429
00:35:00,635 --> 00:35:03,434
在圣诞节前放在店里销售？
to get them into the stores by Christmas?

430
00:35:03,972 --> 00:35:06,039
这对于你来说一定不容易…
It must be terribly embarrassing for you,

431
00:35:06,040 --> 00:35:08,041
我真的很同情，可是…
and I do sympathize. However...

432
00:35:08,042 --> 00:35:09,610
但是我看到他战斗了！
But I saw him fight!

433
00:35:09,611 --> 00:35:11,445
他可以成为有史以来最棒的星空战士！
He could be the greatest Starfighter ever!

434
00:35:11,446 --> 00:35:13,280
那只是个游戏啊，森特利
That was a game, Centauri.

435
00:35:13,281 --> 00:35:14,414
游戏？
A game?

436
00:35:15,516 --> 00:35:18,619
你以为它只是个游戏，但它也是种考验
You may have thought it was a game, but it was also a test.

437
00:35:18,620 --> 00:35:20,387
啊哈！一种考验！
Aha! A test!

438
00:35:20,388 --> 00:35:24,958
它被发向宇宙，寻找那些具有天赋的人成为星空战士
Sent out across the universe to find those with the gift to be Starfighters.

439
00:35:24,959 --> 00:35:27,961
所以你就在这儿了，我的孩子！
And here you are, my boy. Here you are!

440
00:35:27,962 --> 00:35:29,730
没错，我是在这儿了。等着被杀！
Right! Here I am, about to be killed!

441
00:35:29,731 --> 00:35:30,831
被杀…
Killed.

442
00:35:32,500 --> 00:35:35,903
你该不会以为它很危险吧？
You don't seriously think it's dangerous, do you?

443
00:35:35,904 --> 00:35:38,338
别傻了，相信我吧！
Don't be silly! Trust me!

444
00:35:56,591 --> 00:35:57,717
祖尔！
Xur!

445
00:35:58,526 --> 00:35:59,550
祖尔！
Xur!

446
00:36:00,828 --> 00:36:02,057
祖尔？
Xur?

447
00:36:03,631 --> 00:36:08,694
是的，父亲，你那强大的边境现在正在削弱
Yes, Father, your mighty Frontier grows weaker by the moment.

448
00:36:09,804 --> 00:36:12,740
别叫我父亲！
Do not call me father!

449
00:36:13,474 --> 00:36:15,943
我没有你这个儿子！
You are no longer my son!

450
00:36:15,944 --> 00:36:19,243
你已经被我遗弃，为什么还回来？
You're an outcast! Why have you returned?

451
00:36:19,681 --> 00:36:22,683
为了所有赖仑星人好，我回来了
I have returned for the good of all Rylans.

452
00:36:22,684 --> 00:36:26,153
带着柯-旦战舰回来？
With an armada of Ko-Dan warships behind you?

453
00:36:26,154 --> 00:36:29,790
有些赖仑星人会欢迎我的，父亲
There are some Rylans who would welcome me, Father.

454
00:36:29,791 --> 00:36:33,694
星球联盟的正义容不得你这邪教！
Star League justice put down your Xurian cult.

455
00:36:33,695 --> 00:36:36,129
你的追随者既少又分散
Your followers are few and scattered.

456
00:36:36,130 --> 00:36:38,332
星际联盟？
Star League?

457
00:36:38,333 --> 00:36:41,902
只不过是个弱小世界的避难所，根本无法与我们匹敌！
A refuge for weak worlds not worthy to be our equals!

458
00:36:41,903 --> 00:36:44,438
那也是由赖仑星人来作决定
That is for the Rylans to decide,

459
00:36:44,439 --> 00:36:48,398
而不是由像你自己一样的一个既危险又邪恶的孩子来决定！
and not for a dangerous and evil child such as yourself.

460
00:36:50,111 --> 00:36:54,878
然而，也就是这个孩子，捕获了你的主要间谍
And yet, it is this child who caught your master spy.

461
00:37:24,445 --> 00:37:26,106
听我的吧，赖仑星人！
Hear me, Rylans!

462
00:37:27,982 --> 00:37:33,250
当戈兰星的绿月黯然失色的时候，柯-旦的军队将会入侵
When the green moon of Galan is eclipsed, Ko-Dan Armada will invade,

463
00:37:34,956 --> 00:37:39,693
就算你们强大的星空战士也救不了你们
and not even your mighty Starfighters will be able to save you.

464
00:37:39,694 --> 00:37:43,130
我们走着瞧，祖尔。我们走着瞧！
We shall see, Xur. We shall see!

465
00:37:56,077 --> 00:37:57,744
你仍然想走吗？
You still want to go?

466
00:37:57,745 --> 00:37:59,304
想错过这里的精彩？
And miss all the excitement?

467
00:38:05,253 --> 00:38:06,453
小屁孩儿
Little brat.

468
00:38:06,454 --> 00:38:08,855
我发明了游戏，找到了那个孩子，带他过去…
I invent the game, find the kid, drag him up there,

469
00:38:08,856 --> 00:38:11,358
他竟然不想成为星空战士
and he doesn't want to be a Starfighter.

470
00:38:11,359 --> 00:38:12,792
我也算放弃了！
I give up!

471
00:38:49,263 --> 00:38:53,359
Control, do you copy our star angle difference from parking angle?

472
00:38:54,535 --> 00:38:59,132
Delta beta two at six, delta gamma three at five.

473
00:39:04,712 --> 00:39:07,704
祖尔王命令我把他的权杖拿来
Emperor Xur ordered me to bring his scepter.

474
00:39:09,751 --> 00:39:11,451
让他进来
Let him enter.

475
00:39:11,452 --> 00:39:13,921
目标位置仍可见
Target vector remains on scope.

476
00:39:28,603 --> 00:39:32,139
就像你们柯-旦王的一样，对吧，克里尔指挥长？
Just like your Ko-Dan emperor's, isn't it, Commander Kril?

477
00:39:32,140 --> 00:39:38,375
想要统治，单单靠权杖是办不到的，祖尔
It takes more than a scepter to rule, Xur, even on Rylos.

478
00:39:41,115 --> 00:39:42,810
你说得没错，克里尔
You're right, Kril.

479
00:39:44,652 --> 00:39:47,144
单靠权杖的确办不到
It does take more than a scepter.

480
00:39:55,930 --> 00:39:58,399
我们忍这个蠢货要忍多久？
How long must we endure this fool?

481
00:40:00,368 --> 00:40:02,302
边境出现情况
We have a break in the Frontier.

482
00:40:02,303 --> 00:40:04,067
发射流星弹！
Fire the meteor gun!

483
00:40:05,673 --> 00:40:09,910
我亲爱的柯-旦朋友！惟恐我们忘记…
My dear Ko-Dan friends! Lest we forget,

484
00:40:09,911 --> 00:40:13,847
是你们的王委任我担任本军的指挥
it was your own emperor who granted me command of this Armada.

485
00:40:13,848 --> 00:40:16,749
因为只有我才知道通往边境的路
For only I hold the secret to the Frontier.

486
00:40:17,518 --> 00:40:20,253
也只有我才知道星空战士基地
Only I know the location of the Starfighter base.

487
00:40:20,254 --> 00:40:23,952
因此，只有我才有权命令开火！
And therefore, only I will give the order to fire!

488
00:40:28,262 --> 00:40:30,094
请原谅我，祖尔
Forgive me, Xur.

489
00:40:36,571 --> 00:40:39,005
我原谅你，克里尔指挥长
You are forgiven, Commander Kril.

490
00:40:42,577 --> 00:40:46,035
流星弹…发射！
Meteor gunner...fire.

491
00:41:19,080 --> 00:41:20,377
中士！
Sergeant!

492
00:41:22,817 --> 00:41:26,549
三十一区有不明飞行物侵入，长官
I have an unidentified incoming object in Sector 31 , sir.

493
00:41:30,758 --> 00:41:33,493
它们的目标是基地！警戒状态！
They're headed for the base! Alert!

494
00:41:33,494 --> 00:41:34,761
我们受到攻击！
We are under attack!

495
00:41:34,762 --> 00:41:37,129
重复一遍，我们受到攻击！
I repeat, we are under attack!

496
00:41:38,199 --> 00:41:40,668
开启自动排斥枪！
Activate automatic repulser guns.

497
00:42:34,755 --> 00:42:37,884
警戒状态！警戒状态！
Condition Red! Condition Red!

498
00:42:46,934 --> 00:42:48,834
终于成功了！
At last, it is done!

499
00:42:50,404 --> 00:42:52,634
不久，边境将瓦解…
Soon the Frontier will be down

500
00:42:52,773 --> 00:42:55,037
他们也将向他们的新帝王俯首称臣！
and they will bow to their new emperor!

501
00:42:56,043 --> 00:42:57,744
否则，我就用他们的灰烬抹灰天空！
Or I will darken the sky with their ashes.

502
00:42:57,745 --> 00:42:59,713
指挥长，祖尔的间谍报告说…
Commander, the Xurian spy reports

503
00:42:59,714 --> 00:43:01,648
有一个星空战士逃跑了
that one Starfighter has escaped.

504
00:43:02,550 --> 00:43:03,915
逃跑？
Escaped?

505
00:43:16,864 --> 00:43:18,164
你确定不需要我帮忙？
You sure I can't give you a hand?

506
00:43:18,165 --> 00:43:20,300
你已经帮得够多的了。谢谢
You've done quite enough already. Thank you.

507
00:43:20,301 --> 00:43:21,461
那…
Well...

508
00:43:23,270 --> 00:43:25,271
反正也就几公里远了，我想……
It's only a few more miles from here. I guess...

509
00:43:25,272 --> 00:43:27,340
我想我就走回去吧
I guess I can walk it.

510
00:43:27,341 --> 00:43:30,538
后会有期！再见，森特利！
So long! Bye, Centauri!

511
00:43:42,757 --> 00:43:44,520
哦，亚里克斯！
Oh, Alex!

512
00:43:46,494 --> 00:43:47,586
给你！
Here!

513
00:43:52,066 --> 00:43:54,167
嘿，听着。我不能拿你的礼物，森特利
Hey, listen. I can't take a present from you, Centauri.

514
00:43:55,403 --> 00:43:56,770
他把我变得倾家荡产…
He reduces me to poverty again

515
00:43:56,771 --> 00:43:58,438
他还认为我是给他礼物！
and he thinks I'm giving him a present.

516
00:43:58,439 --> 00:43:59,668
什么世道啊？
What a world this is.

517
00:43:59,807 --> 00:44:01,141
那它是什么？
What is it, then?

518
00:44:01,142 --> 00:44:03,143
那是另一次机会，我的孩子！
It's a second chance, my boy!

519
00:44:03,144 --> 00:44:06,511
如果你改变了主意，按下通讯按钮就可以了
If you change your mind, just tap the communo-crystals.

520
00:44:11,085 --> 00:44:13,620
-你留着它吧 -亚里克斯，亚里克斯！
Keep it. Alex, Alex!

521
00:44:13,621 --> 00:44:16,623
你正在背离历史。历史！
You're walking away from history. History!

522
00:44:16,624 --> 00:44:20,193
哥伦布说过他想呆在家里吗？没有！
Did Chris Columbus say he wanted to stay home? No!

523
00:44:20,194 --> 00:44:22,896
要是赖特兄弟认为只有鸟儿才会飞翔会怎么样呢？
What if the Wright Brothers thought that only birds should fly?

524
00:44:22,897 --> 00:44:26,766
吉罗卡有没有认为尤鲁士人丑得无药可救呢？
And did Geloca think the Yulus were too ugly to save?

525
00:44:26,767 --> 00:44:28,235
谁是吉罗卡？
Who's Geloca?

526
00:44:30,104 --> 00:44:31,469
不管了
Never mind.

527
00:44:33,107 --> 00:44:34,474
听着，森特利。我不是他们中的任何一个
Listen, Centauri. I'm not any of those guys.

528
00:44:34,475 --> 00:44:36,042
我只是一个来自拖车场的孩子
I'm a kid from a trailer park.

529
00:44:36,043 --> 00:44:39,673
如果你真是那样想的话，那你也就这样了！
If that's what you think, then that's all you'll ever be!

530
00:45:10,411 --> 00:45:11,844
嘿，玛姬！
Hey, Maggie!

531
00:45:13,647 --> 00:45:15,582
快听听，你绝不会相信的
Listen to this. You're not going to believe this.

532
00:45:16,484 --> 00:45:17,650
我说过了，亚里克斯
I told you, Alex.

533
00:45:17,651 --> 00:45:18,785
我和我的…你是怎么说的来着？
Me and my... How did you put it?

534
00:45:18,786 --> 00:45:22,222
“奇怪的性冲动”再也不会和你说话了！
"Strange sexual urges," aren't talking to you anymore.

535
00:46:03,063 --> 00:46:04,197
谁？
Who's there!

536
00:46:04,198 --> 00:46:06,496
嘘！你会把路易斯吵醒的
Shh! You're gonna wake up Louis.

537
00:46:15,342 --> 00:46:17,174
嘿！你看上去就和我一样！
Hey, you look like me!

538
00:46:17,311 --> 00:46:19,143
当然，我是你的替身
Of course I do. I'm the beta unit.

539
00:46:20,181 --> 00:46:22,376
替身是什么玩意儿？
What the hell's a beta unit?

540
00:46:22,683 --> 00:46:28,747
替身是一个模拟体，一个你的完全的复制体，只是嗓门没那么大
A beta unit is a simuloid, an exact duplicate of you, only not as loud.

541
00:46:30,224 --> 00:46:31,357
啊？
Huh?

542
00:46:31,358 --> 00:46:32,692
我就在汽车里，不记得了？
I was in the starcar, remember?

543
00:46:32,693 --> 00:46:34,027
我们握过手？
We shook hands?

544
00:46:34,028 --> 00:46:36,428
很不幸的是，我成了你
I became you, unfortunately.

545
00:46:38,232 --> 00:46:40,530
说白了，你就是个机器人？
Let me get this straight. You're a robot?

546
00:46:40,768 --> 00:46:42,793
你说什么？
I beg your pardon.

547
00:46:43,504 --> 00:46:47,307
我是一个既有艺术性，又是行业内顶尖级的替身……
I'm a state-of-the-art, top-of-the-line beta unit,

548
00:46:47,308 --> 00:46:51,044
被放到这儿，当你不在的时候顶替你
put here as a courtesy replacement for while you're away.

549
00:46:51,045 --> 00:46:52,912
我还真幸运啊
Lucky me.

550
00:46:52,913 --> 00:46:54,847
等等，你怎么回来了？
Wait a minute. What are you doing back?

551
00:46:54,848 --> 00:46:56,616
你开什么玩笑？那里在打仗！
Are you kidding? It's war up there!

552
00:46:56,617 --> 00:46:59,678
哦，拯救鲸鱼却不拯救整个宇宙，啊？
Oh. Save the whales and not the universe, huh?

553
00:47:00,421 --> 00:47:02,355
那你为什么不去打仗？
Well, why don't you go up there and fight?

554
00:47:02,356 --> 00:47:04,958
模拟体不能打仗。这是不允许的
Simuloids can't fight. We're not allowed.

555
00:47:04,959 --> 00:47:07,359
那告诉他们你就是我。假装嘛！
Well, tell them that you're me! Pretend!

556
00:47:07,494 --> 00:47:09,996
安静点，亚里克斯
Be quiet, Alex.

557
00:47:09,997 --> 00:47:11,658
对不起，路易斯
Sorry, Louis.

558
00:47:12,766 --> 00:47:14,133
谢谢你的礼物！
Thanks for the lift!

559
00:47:14,134 --> 00:47:15,534
别客气，伙计。再见！
Sure thing, buddy. See you around!

560
00:47:38,158 --> 00:47:40,093
你好，星空战士！
Greetings, Starfighter.

561
00:47:40,094 --> 00:47:42,528
你已被星空联盟录取
You have been recruited by the Star League

562
00:47:42,529 --> 00:47:44,828
誓死保卫边境…
to defend the Frontier against Yur and...

563
00:48:05,653 --> 00:48:07,220
那…嘿！你对玛姬做了什么？
And, hey, what did you do to Maggie?

564
00:48:07,221 --> 00:48:08,721
对她？
Do to her?

565
00:48:08,722 --> 00:48:10,223
我们坐在外面，看着星空…
We're sitting outside, looking at the stars,

566
00:48:10,224 --> 00:48:12,249
她把舌头伸到我耳朵里来
and she sticks her tongue in my ear.

567
00:48:12,993 --> 00:48:15,862
我尖叫起来。我明天道歉总好了吧？
I screamed. I'll apologize tomorrow, okay?

568
00:48:15,863 --> 00:48:17,363
你不该在这儿的！
You're not gonna be here.

569
00:48:17,364 --> 00:48:19,094
你现在就得和森特利一起回去！
You're going back with Centauri right now!

570
00:48:19,500 --> 00:48:20,600
怎么了，亚里克斯？
What's up, Alex?

571
00:48:20,601 --> 00:48:23,696
回去睡觉，路易斯。不然我就告诉妈妈你和你那些《花花公子》的事
Back to sleep, Louis, or I'm telling Ma about your Playboys.

572
00:48:26,040 --> 00:48:27,268
你把事情搞砸了，亚里克斯！
You're blowing it, Alex!

573
00:48:32,479 --> 00:48:34,213
怎么回事！
What the shit?

574
00:48:34,214 --> 00:48:37,446
我说了快回去睡觉，路易斯。不然我就告诉妈妈你和你那些《花花公子》的事
I said, back to sleep, Louis, or I'm telling Ma about your Playboys!

575
00:48:39,553 --> 00:48:41,248
拜托，森特利
Come in, Centauri.

576
00:48:42,256 --> 00:48:43,323
拜托，快回来
Come on. Get back here.

577
00:48:43,324 --> 00:48:45,087
把你的仿真玩具带走
And take your Tonka toy with you.

578
00:48:45,959 --> 00:48:47,794
你好，星空战士！
Greetings, Starfighter.

579
00:48:47,795 --> 00:48:51,164
你已被星空联盟录取，誓死保卫边境
You have been recruited by the Star League to defend the Frontier

580
00:48:51,165 --> 00:48:53,895
抗击约和柯-旦舰队的入侵
against Yur and the Ko-Dan Armada.

581
00:48:54,802 --> 00:48:56,569
你好，星空战士！
Greetings, Starfighter.

582
00:48:56,570 --> 00:48:58,037
你已被星空联盟录取…
You have been recruited by the Star League

583
00:48:58,038 --> 00:49:00,439
誓死保卫边境…
to defend the Frontier against Yur...

584
00:49:05,179 --> 00:49:07,814
你在哪儿？出来啊？你在哪儿？
Where are you? Come on, where are you?

585
00:49:07,815 --> 00:49:09,146
森特利？
Centauri?

586
00:49:10,117 --> 00:49:12,017
你好，星空战士！
Greetings, Starfighter!

587
00:49:13,220 --> 00:49:14,517
森特利？
Centauri?

588
00:50:16,650 --> 00:50:18,184
哦，不好！
Oh, shit!

589
00:50:18,185 --> 00:50:20,019
来啊，亚里克斯，别那么懦弱！
Come on, Alex. Don't be such a wimp!

590
00:50:37,738 --> 00:50:38,938
森特利，当心！
Centauri, look out!

591
00:50:38,939 --> 00:50:40,100
怎么回事…
What the...

592
00:51:06,967 --> 00:51:08,025
Phew!

593
00:51:08,202 --> 00:51:11,000
肮脏、恶臭的生物
Foul stench. Dirty creatures.

594
00:51:15,576 --> 00:51:17,276
好好看看，亚里克斯
Get a good look, Alex.

595
00:51:17,277 --> 00:51:20,513
我敢打赌你以后会看见更多
You can bet your asteroids you'll be seeing more of them.

596
00:51:20,514 --> 00:51:21,781
什么？
What?

597
00:51:21,782 --> 00:51:23,215
这是赞多-赞
This is a Zando-Zan.

598
00:51:23,584 --> 00:51:26,576
一种星际怪物，祖尔的走狗
An interstellar hitbeast, compliments of Xur.

599
00:51:27,321 --> 00:51:29,789
祖尔？他为什么要跟踪我？
Xur? Why is he after me?

600
00:51:29,790 --> 00:51:32,124
不知为什么，他发现你是一个星空战士
Somehow he found out you're a Starfighter.

601
00:51:32,125 --> 00:51:35,828
所以，你看，亚里克斯，你得回去。你别无选择
So you see, Alex, you got to go back. You got no choice.

602
00:51:35,829 --> 00:51:37,797
你要是呆在这里的话，你就变成它们的事物了
'Cause if you stay down here, you're dog food.

603
00:51:37,798 --> 00:51:39,532
相信森特利，我的孩子
Trust Centauri, my boy.

604
00:51:39,533 --> 00:51:43,803
因为两小时以后，这个地方将爬满十只赞多-赞s…
Because in two hours, this place will be crawling with 10 Zando-Zans

605
00:51:43,804 --> 00:51:47,807
它们那木鱼脑子里只有一个目的…
with just one thought on their microscopic little minds,

606
00:51:47,808 --> 00:51:49,475
杀死亚里克斯罗根
kill Alex Rogan.

607
00:51:49,476 --> 00:51:51,110
杀死亚里克斯罗根
Kill Alex Rogan.

608
00:51:51,111 --> 00:51:52,612
他说得没错，亚里克斯
He's right, Alex.

609
00:51:52,613 --> 00:51:55,348
至少在那里你还有机会在刚星里面战斗
At least up there you'll have a fighting chance in a Gunstar.

610
00:51:55,349 --> 00:51:56,516
没错
Exactly.

611
00:51:56,517 --> 00:51:59,585
同时，在这儿，他们会追杀替身
Meanwhile, down here, they'll be going after Beta.

612
00:51:59,586 --> 00:52:01,187
-替身 -替身？
Beta. Beta?

613
00:52:01,188 --> 00:52:03,189
当然。不然你以为他是干什么来的？
Of course. What do you think he's here for?

614
00:52:03,190 --> 00:52:06,058
等…等等，森特利
Wait a... Wait a second here, Centauri.

615
00:52:06,059 --> 00:52:07,360
亚里克斯，当心！
Alex, look out!

616
00:52:15,202 --> 00:52:16,601
森特利！
Centauri!

617
00:52:17,905 --> 00:52:19,038
替身，去叫医生！
Beta, get a doctor!

618
00:52:19,039 --> 00:52:21,474
不，这里看不好的，因为没有巫医
No. No native cures. No witch doctors.

619
00:52:21,909 --> 00:52:24,207
我没事，只是擦伤
I'm fine. Just a scratch.

620
00:52:27,180 --> 00:52:30,639
面对现实吧，亚里克斯。你天生就是个星空战士
Now face it, Alex. You're a born Starfighter.

621
00:52:33,253 --> 00:52:34,846
跟我去吗？
Are you with me?

622
00:52:44,531 --> 00:52:46,522
好吧，我们走，森特利
Okay, let's go, Centauri.

623
00:52:48,869 --> 00:52:50,428
祝你好运，亚里克斯
Good luck, Alex.

624
00:52:53,473 --> 00:52:55,271
你也是，亚里克斯
You, too, Alex.

625
00:53:18,465 --> 00:53:20,797
森特利呼叫星空战士指挥部
Centauri to Starfighter Command.

626
00:53:21,368 --> 00:53:23,302
森特利呼叫星空战士指挥部
Centauri to Starfighter Command.

627
00:53:23,303 --> 00:53:24,862
请回答
Come in, please.

628
00:53:41,655 --> 00:53:43,179
嘿，森特利
Hey, Centauri.

629
00:53:46,259 --> 00:53:48,127
所有人员注意
Attention all personnel.

630
00:53:48,128 --> 00:53:50,290
星际汽车正在接近十二号停靠点
Starcar is approaching Docking Bay 12.

631
00:53:51,698 --> 00:53:53,997
森特利！森特利！
Centauri! Centauri!

632
00:53:59,139 --> 00:54:00,937
嘿！快踩刹车！
Hey, hit the brakes!

633
00:54:06,613 --> 00:54:08,648
-格里格！嘿，格里格！ -亚里克斯！
Grig! Hey, Grig! Alex!

634
00:54:08,649 --> 00:54:10,650
他们击中了森特利。他受伤了
They got Centauri. He's hurt!

635
00:54:10,651 --> 00:54:12,312
他在这儿
He's right over here.

636
00:54:24,031 --> 00:54:26,090
啊？你看到了？
Ah, you see?

637
00:54:27,534 --> 00:54:29,101
森特利带他回来了！
Centauri brought him back!

638
00:54:29,102 --> 00:54:30,934
-是的，我看见了 -别说话
Yes, I see. Don't talk.

639
00:54:31,805 --> 00:54:33,839
他把我的钱拿回去了吗，亚里克斯？
Does he have my money, Alex?

640
00:54:33,840 --> 00:54:36,469
我有一大笔钱给你，森特利
I have a fortune for you, Centauri.

641
00:54:36,777 --> 00:54:38,411
你现在要坚持住
Now, please be still.

642
00:54:39,813 --> 00:54:42,942
钱在这儿，全在这儿。一叠一叠的钱
It's here. It's all here. Piles and piles of it.

643
00:54:44,051 --> 00:54:45,484
都是你的
All for you.

644
00:54:46,319 --> 00:54:47,787
啊…
Ah...

645
00:54:48,889 --> 00:54:50,152
终于
At last.

646
00:54:52,592 --> 00:54:58,122
亚里克斯，我要你知道，能把你带回来是最幸运的事
Alex, I want you know, it was for the greatest good I brought you back.

647
00:55:00,734 --> 00:55:04,102
当然，想…
Of course, it...

648
00:55:04,771 --> 00:55:07,070
想要有钱也要付出点代价
It never hurts to be rich.

649
00:55:17,017 --> 00:55:21,079
一路走好，老朋友
Until the next dimension, old friend.

650
00:55:23,623 --> 00:55:25,319
很遗憾，亚里克斯
I'm sorry, Alex.

651
00:55:26,026 --> 00:55:27,323
森特利？
Centauri?

652
00:55:33,033 --> 00:55:34,364
森特利？
Centauri?

653
00:55:36,069 --> 00:55:38,936
边境任何时候都有可能瓦解
The Frontier could collapse at any moment.

654
00:55:39,739 --> 00:55:41,173
亚里克斯！
Alex!

655
00:56:37,764 --> 00:56:41,428
现在我的耳朵需要次手术。几乎听不到声音了
Now I need an earjob. Dying here. Dying.

656
00:56:56,383 --> 00:57:00,119
亚里克斯，究竟发生了什么？
Alex, what the hell's going on?

657
00:57:00,120 --> 00:57:03,317
路易斯，你正在做恶梦
Louis, you're having a terrible nightmare.

658
00:57:04,124 --> 00:57:05,250
快回去睡觉
Go back to sleep.

659
00:57:09,930 --> 00:57:11,295
路易斯！
Louis!

660
00:57:24,978 --> 00:57:26,468
哦，不
Oh, no.

661
00:57:36,656 --> 00:57:40,226
据我所知，你家里有个替身在顶替你？
Am I to understand there's a beta unit taking your place back home?

662
00:57:40,227 --> 00:57:41,327
他在努力尝试
He's trying.

663
00:57:41,328 --> 00:57:44,496
所以我们完全可以推断，祖尔认为你还在地球上
So it's safe to assume that Xur thinks you're still on Earth.

664
00:57:44,497 --> 00:57:46,365
是啊
Yeah.

665
00:57:46,366 --> 00:57:49,097
那我们在理论上可以算是有优势了
That could work to our advantage, theoretically.

666
00:57:56,109 --> 00:57:58,476
啊！你现在看上去像个人了！
Ah! Now you look human!

667
00:58:01,014 --> 00:58:02,514
这就是我的刚星？
Is this my Gunstar?

668
00:58:02,515 --> 00:58:05,050
这只是个样品，和其他飞船有点区别
This is a prototype, different from the other ships.

669
00:58:05,051 --> 00:58:06,919
她有更远的射程，更大的威力…
She has a greater range, more power,

670
00:58:06,920 --> 00:58:09,048
同时，也作了轻微的装备改良
and a slight weapons modification.

671
00:58:10,257 --> 00:58:12,024
当然，她还有防护层
And, of course, she's got deflective plating,

672
00:58:12,025 --> 00:58:14,460
所以她经得起几次直接攻击
so she can withstand several direct hits.

673
00:58:19,833 --> 00:58:22,101
我就是从这里，为飞船导航
From here, this is where I navigate the ship,

674
00:58:22,102 --> 00:58:25,094
维护维生系统和推进系统
maintain life support and propulsion systems.

675
00:58:26,506 --> 00:58:27,840
那我坐在哪儿？
Okay. Where do I sit?

676
00:58:27,841 --> 00:58:30,367
在那边，发射席上
Way up there, in the gunnery chair.

677
00:58:33,613 --> 00:58:34,913
站稳了！
Hang on!

678
00:58:34,914 --> 00:58:35,938
好的
Okay.

679
00:58:41,187 --> 00:58:43,952
现在，爬到发射席上
Now, climb into the gunnery chair.

680
00:58:45,191 --> 00:58:48,855
我将你设置为发射状态
Now, I'm moving you into launch position.

681
00:58:50,363 --> 00:58:52,264
在你前面有两个开关…
There in front of you are the two switches

682
00:58:52,265 --> 00:58:54,563
可以打开显示器。现在打开它们
for your heads-up display. Turn them on.

683
00:58:59,072 --> 00:59:00,339
当你和敌人交战时…
While you're engaging the enemy,

684
00:59:00,340 --> 00:59:03,969
显示器会向你显示所有接近你的战舰
the screen will reflect all battle instruments towards you.

685
00:59:05,912 --> 00:59:06,979
嘿，它哪儿去了？
Hey, where did it go?

686
00:59:06,980 --> 00:59:09,648
它还在那儿，飘浮在氖气雾霭中
It's still there, suspended in a xenon mist.

687
00:59:09,649 --> 00:59:11,650
你只要以正确的角度看就能看到
But it's only visible if you look dead ahead.

688
00:59:11,651 --> 00:59:13,620
哦，看到了
Ah. Got it.

689
00:59:13,787 --> 00:59:15,821
你左面的操纵杆是操纵你的座椅的
The lever on your left is the chair controller.

690
00:59:15,822 --> 00:59:19,122
你可以看到，所有的枪都跟着你一起移动
As you can see, all guns will track with your every move.

691
00:59:26,866 --> 00:59:30,069
右手抓紧瞄准器
Grasp the target control with your right hand.

692
00:59:30,070 --> 00:59:33,706
你的手指可以操纵所有机枪――激光枪、霹雳弹…
At your fingers is the weaponry, the lasers, photon bolts...

693
00:59:33,707 --> 00:59:34,940
还有粒子射线
Photon bolts and the particle beams.

694
00:59:34,941 --> 00:59:36,602
等等，这和我在家玩的一样啊
Wait a minute. This is just like back home.

695
00:59:37,210 --> 00:59:38,677
-这是什么？ -当心，当心…
What's this? Careful, careful,

696
00:59:38,678 --> 00:59:42,047
那是死亡霸王花，最后关头才能用
that's Death Blossom, a weapon of last resort.

697
00:59:42,048 --> 00:59:45,284
幸运的是，我不小心触动它的时候飞机库正在上升
Luckily, I was in here working on it when the hangar went up.

698
00:59:45,285 --> 00:59:48,345
准备好了吗？所有系统，开启！
Now, are you ready? All systems, go!

699
00:59:50,457 --> 00:59:51,754
点火！
Ignition!

700
00:59:55,729 --> 00:59:57,663
飞机库什么时候上升？
When did the hangar go up?

701
00:59:57,664 --> 01:00:00,599
我说过了，当祖尔袭击我们的时候！
I told you, when Xur attacked.

702
01:00:00,767 --> 01:00:02,034
那星空战士都在哪儿？
And where were the Starfighters?

703
01:00:02,035 --> 01:00:03,235
在飞机库里！
In the hangar!

704
01:00:03,236 --> 01:00:05,004
你是说他们都死了？
You mean they're dead?

705
01:00:05,005 --> 01:00:07,064
死是个消极的概念
Death is a primitive concept.

706
01:00:08,074 --> 01:00:12,945
我宁可认为他们在另一空间与邪恶而战
I prefer to think of them as battling evil in another dimension.

707
01:00:12,946 --> 01:00:15,714
在另一空间？有多少人离开了？
In another dimension? How many are left?

708
01:00:15,715 --> 01:00:16,944
包括你自己？
Including yourself?

709
01:00:17,417 --> 01:00:18,646
对
Yeah.

710
01:00:19,919 --> 01:00:21,182
一个！
One!

711
01:00:22,255 --> 01:00:23,313
一个？
One?

712
01:00:34,601 --> 01:00:35,898
等等！
Hold it.

713
01:00:38,738 --> 01:00:41,607
我们没有舰队，没有星空战士，连个计划也没有？
There's no fleet, no Starfighters, no plan?

714
01:00:41,608 --> 01:00:44,042
-一艘飞船，你，我，没了？ -完全正确！
One ship, you, me, and that's it? Exactly!

715
01:00:44,043 --> 01:00:45,244
祖尔认为你还在地球上
Xur thinks you're still on Earth.

716
01:00:45,245 --> 01:00:47,446
经典战略：突袭
Classic military strategy. Surprise attack.

717
01:00:47,447 --> 01:00:48,714
那简直是送死！
It'll be a slaughter!

718
01:00:48,715 --> 01:00:50,182
要的就是这种精神！
That's the spirit.

719
01:00:50,183 --> 01:00:51,683
不，是我去送死！
No, my slaughter.

720
01:00:51,684 --> 01:00:53,685
一艘飞船对抗整个部队？
One ship against the whole Armada?

721
01:00:53,686 --> 01:00:57,122
对。一架刚星对抗整个部队！
Yes. One Gunstar against the Armada.

722
01:00:57,123 --> 01:01:01,959
我总是想和不可思议的敌人来一场破釜沉舟的战斗！
I've always wanted to fight a desperate battle against incredible odds.

723
01:01:04,697 --> 01:01:05,998
搜索目标，亚里克斯
Target lights, Alex.

724
01:01:05,999 --> 01:01:07,199
搜索目标？
Target lights?

725
01:01:07,200 --> 01:01:09,001
没错。你总得在还有机会的时候…
Yes. You might want to squeeze off

726
01:01:09,002 --> 01:01:10,736
多打它几个回合吧？
a few rounds while you have the chance.

727
01:01:10,737 --> 01:01:12,838
发挥飞船的最大攻击力
Just work the bugs out of the system.

728
01:01:12,839 --> 01:01:14,967
毕竟，这是她的处女航
After all, it is her maiden voyage.

729
01:01:36,429 --> 01:01:38,664
稳住，别和座椅过不去
Steady. Don't fight the chair.

730
01:01:38,665 --> 01:01:40,599
慢慢来。用枪瞄准
Take your time. Watch your gun sights.

731
01:01:40,600 --> 01:01:42,501
看好目标
Lead your targets.

732
01:01:42,502 --> 01:01:44,834
总之，放松就是了！
And above all, relax!

733
01:01:45,405 --> 01:01:48,640
真好，我就要被杀得片甲不留…
Terrific. I'm about to get killed a million miles from nowhere

734
01:01:48,641 --> 01:01:51,611
竟然还有一个蜥蜴人叫我“放松”！
with a gung-ho iguana who tells me, "Relax."

735
01:01:54,781 --> 01:01:56,271
星空战士！
Interstellar!

736
01:02:29,115 --> 01:02:30,310
亚里克斯！
Alex!

737
01:02:31,017 --> 01:02:32,246
对不起
Sorry.

738
01:02:34,854 --> 01:02:37,721
好的，来，慢慢举起来
Okay, now, come on. Ease it up.

739
01:02:39,626 --> 01:02:40,820
好的
Okay.

740
01:02:42,595 --> 01:02:45,224
哦，行…行了！简单
Oh, that's... That's it. Easy.

741
01:02:45,765 --> 01:02:47,563
漂亮又简单
Nice and easy. Yep.

742
01:02:48,301 --> 01:02:51,703
再过来点就能装好了
A little bit more and we'll get it in there, now.

743
01:02:52,839 --> 01:02:53,999
亚里克斯！
Alex!

744
01:02:55,775 --> 01:02:58,744
对不起。嗨，玛姬
Sorry. Hi, Maggs.

745
01:02:58,745 --> 01:03:00,012
亚里克斯，你没事吧？
Alex, are you all right?

746
01:03:00,013 --> 01:03:02,277
是啊，是啊。我…没事
Yeah. Yeah, I'm... I'm fine.

747
01:03:03,783 --> 01:03:06,252
快点，再来一次
Come on. Try it again.

748
01:03:07,787 --> 01:03:09,653
你闻到什么了吗？
Did you smell anything?

749
01:03:11,324 --> 01:03:12,382
什么？
Like what?

750
01:03:12,525 --> 01:03:13,617
就像…
Like a Z...

751
01:03:14,727 --> 01:03:16,059
算了
Forget it.

752
01:03:24,037 --> 01:03:27,769
我只是想为昨天晚上给你的巴掌道歉
I just wanted to say I'm sorry for slapping you last night.

753
01:03:29,008 --> 01:03:31,877
哦，没关系，玛姬。我活该
Oh, that's okay, Maggs. I deserved it.

754
01:03:31,878 --> 01:03:33,607
抱歉
I'm sorry.

755
01:03:33,813 --> 01:03:37,943
要不…我们今晚去银湖弥补一下？
Well, maybe we can make it up to each other tonight at Silver Lake?

756
01:04:07,180 --> 01:04:09,715
敌军将会从这里进入边境
The Armada will break through the Frontier here,

757
01:04:09,716 --> 01:04:12,217
二十公里后到达赖罗斯
and reach Rylos in 20 klicks.

758
01:04:12,218 --> 01:04:15,053
甲板上的空中部队将跟随母舰
Squadrons of deck fighters will precede the mother ship.

759
01:04:15,054 --> 01:04:16,955
空中部队？有多少空中部队？
Squadrons? How many squadrons?

760
01:04:16,956 --> 01:04:19,257
数量我倒不在乎
It isn't the number of squadrons that concerns me.

761
01:04:19,258 --> 01:04:21,193
这座通信塔将指令…
It's this communication turret that sends out

762
01:04:21,194 --> 01:04:22,794
发送给空中部队
the commands to the deck fighters,

763
01:04:22,795 --> 01:04:25,097
这样，他们就能同时作战
which enables them to act as one during the fight.

764
01:04:25,098 --> 01:04:27,866
等等，我们摧毁塔台以破坏空中部队
Wait a second. We knock out the turret to get the fighters.

765
01:04:27,867 --> 01:04:30,469
但是要摧毁塔台，我们就要穿过空中部队？
But to get the turret, we have to get through the fighters.

766
01:04:30,470 --> 01:04:31,903
那我们就死了
We're dead.

767
01:04:31,904 --> 01:04:34,840
在到达边境前我会想出办法的
I'll have it all figured out by the time we reach the Frontier.

768
01:04:37,877 --> 01:04:39,111
怎么了？
What's that?

769
01:04:39,112 --> 01:04:40,170
是边境
The Frontier.

770
01:04:49,522 --> 01:04:51,623
真是奇怪，运输舰…
Now, that's strange. What's a cargo ship

771
01:04:51,624 --> 01:04:53,422
在边境附近干什么？
doing this close to the Frontier?

772
01:04:54,327 --> 01:04:57,023
你好，这里是刚星一号
Hail. This is Gunstar One.

773
01:05:01,734 --> 01:05:03,635
重复，这里是刚星一号
I repeat, this is Gunstar One.

774
01:05:03,636 --> 01:05:05,798
请确认身份
Identify yourself, please.

775
01:05:08,041 --> 01:05:09,599
亚里克斯，当心！
Alex, look out.

776
01:05:12,745 --> 01:05:14,213
是祖尔的飞船！
A Xurian ship!

777
01:05:16,883 --> 01:05:18,116
恭喜你，亚里克斯
Congratulations, Alex.

778
01:05:18,117 --> 01:05:20,814
这是你第一个活体目标
This is your first live target.

779
01:05:21,020 --> 01:05:22,215
活体？
Live?

780
01:05:25,925 --> 01:05:28,724
五公里后进入射程。准备！
Within range in five klicks. Get ready!

781
01:05:33,533 --> 01:05:35,267
我拦截了他的信号
I've blocked its beam of frequency,

782
01:05:35,268 --> 01:05:37,236
所以他没办法向总部报告
so it can't report back to the Armada.

783
01:05:38,738 --> 01:05:40,501
-准备好了就开火！ -格里格，等等！
Fire when ready! Grig, wait!

784
01:05:50,383 --> 01:05:53,148
我们不能在洞穴里跟丢了，亚里克斯！开火！
We mustn't lose them in these caves, Alex! Fire!

785
01:06:16,442 --> 01:06:17,876
开火，亚里克斯！
Shoot, Alex!

786
01:06:22,482 --> 01:06:25,349
开火！
Shoot!

787
01:06:32,992 --> 01:06:34,226
你成功了！
You did it!

788
01:06:41,200 --> 01:06:43,835
我成功了？是你成功了！
I did it? You did it!

789
01:06:43,836 --> 01:06:45,202
你差点让我送了命！
You almost got me killed!

790
01:06:48,341 --> 01:06:50,503
我最诚意的道歉，亚里克斯
My deepest apologies, Alex.

791
01:06:51,277 --> 01:06:53,712
我原本打算让你经历了枪林弹雨以后…
I had hoped that by putting you in the thick of battle,

792
01:06:53,713 --> 01:06:56,148
一个伟大的星空战士即将诞生
a great Starfighter would emerge.

793
01:06:56,315 --> 01:07:01,583
但是，唉。也许你本来就不是这块料
But, alas. Perhaps there was never one within you to begin with.

794
01:07:04,190 --> 01:07:06,022
我载你回家吧
I shall take you home.

795
01:07:07,326 --> 01:07:10,785
在那儿，你仍可以过上很长一段时间的安稳日子…
You still may live a long and fruitful life back there.

796
01:07:11,564 --> 01:07:14,898
直到柯-旦打到地球
That is, until the Ko-Dan reach Earth.

797
01:07:16,235 --> 01:07:17,302
但到了那个时候…
But then again...

798
01:07:32,351 --> 01:07:35,554
嘿，布雷克！让那破音响再响一点啊！
Hey, yo, Blake! Make that sucker blast, man!

799
01:07:35,555 --> 01:07:38,323
没问题，伙计！
You got it, dude! All right!

800
01:07:44,397 --> 01:07:47,098
布雷克回来是拿他的裤子的对吧？
So Blake comes back in to grab his pants, right?

801
01:07:47,099 --> 01:07:48,934
看到她奶奶，说…
Sees her old lady, and says,

802
01:07:48,935 --> 01:07:51,995
“希望这不会让我星期二晚上没饭吃”
"I hope this doesn't rule out dinner on Tuesday night."

803
01:07:53,806 --> 01:07:55,331
你真搞笑！
That's my man!

804
01:07:59,178 --> 01:08:01,704
亚里克斯，你没事吧？
Alex, are you okay?

805
01:08:01,848 --> 01:08:02,948
啊？
Hmm?

806
01:08:02,949 --> 01:08:05,145
对啊，没事。怎么了？
Yeah, sure. Why?

807
01:08:06,252 --> 01:08:09,421
我不知道，你老是走神
I don't know. You're just acting spaced out.

808
01:08:09,422 --> 01:08:10,889
这…这很不像你啊
You're... You're not yourself.

809
01:08:12,859 --> 01:08:17,956
如果你是我，你现在会怎么办？
Well, if you were me, what would you be doing right now?

810
01:08:21,667 --> 01:08:25,170
首先呢，我会先好好享受生活
Well, for one thing, I'd be trying to enjoy myself.

811
01:08:25,171 --> 01:08:29,174
靠在车上，开开玩笑，大笑
Leaning back. Kidding around. Laughing.

812
01:08:29,175 --> 01:08:30,442
大笑？
Laughing?

813
01:08:30,443 --> 01:08:31,808
这只是个开始，亚里克斯
Well, it's a start, Alex.

814
01:08:32,712 --> 01:08:34,043
大笑
Laughing.

815
01:09:19,292 --> 01:09:22,260
好地方。让我想起我的家
Nice place. Reminds me of home.

816
01:09:22,261 --> 01:09:24,129
这能让你想家？
This reminds you of home?

817
01:09:24,130 --> 01:09:25,825
哦，是啊
Oh, yes.

818
01:09:30,970 --> 01:09:37,569
我和我的妻子和六千个孩子住在地下
I live below ground with my wifeoid and 6,000 little Griglings.

819
01:09:45,351 --> 01:09:48,582
至少，在祖尔把他们变成努力之前
At least, until Xur turns them into slaves.

820
01:09:53,893 --> 01:09:56,157
你们这个物种住在哪儿？
Where does your kind live?

821
01:09:56,295 --> 01:09:58,594
哦，基本上都住在房子里
Oh, uh, houses, mostly.

822
01:09:59,332 --> 01:10:02,961
也就是地上的洞穴。看看这个
That's caves above ground. See, here.

823
01:10:03,569 --> 01:10:06,300
这是我全家
Here's my family.

824
01:10:06,906 --> 01:10:08,396
看，这是…
See, that's...

825
01:10:09,008 --> 01:10:13,070
这是我父母，这是我弟弟，路易斯，这是玛姬
That's my folks and my brother, Louis, and that's Maggie.

826
01:10:15,281 --> 01:10:17,408
我们住在移动的家里
Uh, we live in a mobile home.

827
01:10:19,185 --> 01:10:21,585
就是会去各种地方的洞穴
That's a cave that goes places.

828
01:10:21,887 --> 01:10:24,049
只是我们从来没去过别的地方
Only we never went anyplace.

829
01:10:26,692 --> 01:10:30,895
一个从来不去别处的移动洞穴。有意思
A mobile cave that never went anywhere. Fascinating.

830
01:10:30,896 --> 01:10:34,366
是啊，但是我们在拖车场附近也有底下的洞穴
Yeah, but we have below-ground caves near the trailer parks.

831
01:10:34,367 --> 01:10:37,769
我和我弟弟路易斯过去常常在里面玩捉迷藏…
Me and my brother, Louis, used to play hide-and-seek in them.

832
01:10:39,905 --> 01:10:41,973
捉迷藏
Hide-and-seek.

833
01:10:41,974 --> 01:10:43,041
捉迷藏是什么，亚里克斯？
What is it, Alex?

834
01:10:43,042 --> 01:10:46,745
我在想，也许我们可以躲在这里…
Well, I was just thinking, maybe we could hide here,

835
01:10:46,746 --> 01:10:51,149
等敌军经过的时候，从后方攻击他们的塔台
let the Armada pass by, and then hit the turret from behind.

836
01:10:51,150 --> 01:10:53,710
然后，我们就以突袭的方式打败他们
Then we might take them by surprise.

837
01:10:58,891 --> 01:11:01,192
你的策略也许真能奏效
Your plan might really have worked.

838
01:11:01,193 --> 01:11:05,163
只可惜没有星空战士来执行它了
What a pity there are no Starfighters left to carry it out.

839
01:11:05,164 --> 01:11:06,495
是啊，是啊
Yeah. Yeah.

840
01:11:15,541 --> 01:11:17,100
一个祖尔的基地！
A Xurian base!

841
01:11:35,628 --> 01:11:38,256
正前方还有两个。快速靠近中！
Two more dead ahead! Closing fast!

842
01:12:02,688 --> 01:12:05,783
前往地球的航线已准备完毕
Earth course is logged into navigational beams.

843
01:12:07,560 --> 01:12:08,652
格里格？
Grig?

844
01:12:10,463 --> 01:12:12,055
什么事，亚里克斯？
What is it, Alex?

845
01:12:16,969 --> 01:12:19,438
也许真的只剩下一个星空战士了
Maybe there is a Starfighter left.

846
01:12:58,377 --> 01:12:59,572
啊！
Ow!

847
01:13:07,453 --> 01:13:08,786
怎么了？
What's wrong?

848
01:13:08,787 --> 01:13:10,380
我现在是不是该把我的舌头伸到你耳朵里？
Should I put my tongue in your ear now?

849
01:13:10,856 --> 01:13:12,552
算了，亚里克斯
Don't bother, Alex.

850
01:13:13,159 --> 01:13:14,325
我只是…
Well, it's just...

851
01:13:14,326 --> 01:13:16,022
我只是不习惯这种事…
I'm kind of new at these gland games.

852
01:13:17,663 --> 01:13:19,697
你在说些什么啊？
What are you talking about?

853
01:13:19,698 --> 01:13:22,634
就好像你是从外太空来的，亚里克斯！
It's like you're a million miles away, Alex!

854
01:13:32,344 --> 01:13:34,904
喂，喂，喂，等等啊，宝贝儿
Whoa, whoa, whoa. Wait. Darling.

855
01:13:36,015 --> 01:13:38,245
宝贝儿，原谅我吧
Darling, forgive me.

856
01:13:47,393 --> 01:13:49,225
“宝贝儿，原谅我吧”
"Darling, forgive me."

857
01:13:53,465 --> 01:13:54,797
拜托！
Come on!

858
01:13:55,868 --> 01:13:58,236
你是我的茱丽叶，我的维纳斯
You're my Juliet. My Venus.

859
01:14:02,341 --> 01:14:06,335
“你是我的茱丽叶，我的维纳斯”
"You're my Juliet. My Venus."

860
01:14:09,515 --> 01:14:11,049
亚里克斯！
Alex!

861
01:14:11,050 --> 01:14:13,018
其他女孩儿对我来说都毫无意义
All the other girls meant nothing to me.

862
01:14:13,652 --> 01:14:16,854
我爱的是你啊。你，你
It was you, you, you.

863
01:14:16,855 --> 01:14:19,123
住口，跟我说点脏的
Shut up and talk dirty to me.

864
01:14:20,893 --> 01:14:26,058
“其他女孩儿对我来说都毫无意义。我爱的是你啊。你，你”
"The other girls meant nothing to me. It was you, you..."

865
01:14:27,900 --> 01:14:29,634
我要跟你说点脏的吗？
Should I talk dirty to you now?

866
01:14:30,736 --> 01:14:32,136
够了
That does it.

867
01:14:32,137 --> 01:14:35,107
哦，天啊。好的，我放弃了
Oh, God. All right. I give up.

868
01:14:35,741 --> 01:14:37,275
我不是亚里克斯罗根
I'm not Alex Rogan.

869
01:14:37,276 --> 01:14:38,843
什么？
What?

870
01:14:38,844 --> 01:14:40,044
我只是个替身
I'm a beta unit.

871
01:14:40,045 --> 01:14:41,308
我是亚里克斯的复制品
I'm an exact duplicate of Alex.

872
01:14:41,580 --> 01:14:42,814
他在那儿拯救全宇宙…
He's up there saving the universe,

873
01:14:42,815 --> 01:14:44,612
我在这儿做敌军的诱饵
while I'm down here for target practice.

874
01:14:47,353 --> 01:14:48,581
看到了吧？
See?

875
01:14:57,429 --> 01:14:59,430
亚里克斯！或者不管你是谁，等等，等等
Alex! Or whatever you are. Wait. Wait.

876
01:14:59,431 --> 01:15:00,531
你在干什么？让我走
What are you do... Let me go.

877
01:15:00,532 --> 01:15:01,599
如果那个赞多-赞向总部报告…
If that Zando-Zan reports back

878
01:15:01,600 --> 01:15:03,801
说我不是亚里克斯，亚里克斯就有危险了
that I'm not Alex, Alex is in big trouble!

879
01:15:03,802 --> 01:15:05,136
-你呆在这儿 -不，我不要
You're staying here. No, I'm not.

880
01:15:05,137 --> 01:15:07,731
我哪儿都不要呆直到我弄清楚真相
I'm not staying anywhere until I find out what's going on!

881
01:15:10,175 --> 01:15:12,974
嘿，我的卡车！嘿，嘿，回来！
Hey, my truck! Hey, hey, come back!

882
01:15:15,314 --> 01:15:17,578
有一点点擦坏，你就死定了，罗根！
Scratch that paint, and you're dead, Rogan!

883
01:15:27,860 --> 01:15:29,394
入侵已就绪，指挥长
Ready to invade, Commander.

884
01:15:29,395 --> 01:15:30,495
入侵
Invade.

885
01:15:30,496 --> 01:15:33,665
指挥长，祖尔飞船一直没有回复我们的入侵代码
Commander, the Xurian ships have not answered our invasion code.

886
01:15:33,666 --> 01:15:36,100
边境瓦解了，月亮消失了…
The Frontier is down, the moon is eclipsed,

887
01:15:36,101 --> 01:15:38,434
星空战士都死了。开始入侵吧！
the Starfighters are dead. lnvade!

888
01:15:39,371 --> 01:15:43,240
所有空中部队，半速前进。开启能源探测器
All squadrons ahead, half speed, with energy probes on.

889
01:16:13,872 --> 01:16:16,705
能源探测器。快关闭，亚里克斯。关闭
Energy probe. Shut down, Alex. Shut down.

890
01:16:17,943 --> 01:16:19,274
关闭
Power off.

891
01:16:35,995 --> 01:16:38,225
亚里克斯在太空中？
Alex? ln space?

892
01:16:40,899 --> 01:16:43,534
-真的假的？ -真的！我不是一直在跟你说嘛
Is this for real? - Yes! That's what I'm trying to tell you!

893
01:16:43,535 --> 01:16:44,836
全是真的！
It's all for real!

894
01:16:44,837 --> 01:16:46,430
那别说话了，开车啊！
Well, then, don't talk. Drive!

895
01:16:59,685 --> 01:17:02,887
克里尔指挥长，紧急频率收到信号
Commander Kril, we're getting a signal on the alert frequency.

896
01:17:02,888 --> 01:17:04,288
接收
Acknowledge.

897
01:17:07,793 --> 01:17:09,394
到了。好的
There it is. All right.

898
01:17:09,395 --> 01:17:11,362
等我接近发射器以后你就跳，知道了吗？
Now, when I give the signal, we're gonna jump! Okay?

899
01:17:11,363 --> 01:17:13,297
-“跳”是什么意思？ -我们用车撞掉它
What do you mean, "Jump"? We're gonna ram him.

900
01:17:13,298 --> 01:17:14,288
什么？
What?

901
01:17:15,401 --> 01:17:18,102
灭绝特使六号有一则消息
Extermination Emissary Zeta 6, one message.

902
01:17:18,103 --> 01:17:20,071
准备好了吗？跳！
Ready? Jump!

903
01:17:20,072 --> 01:17:21,506
亚里克斯！
Alex!

904
01:17:23,108 --> 01:17:25,042
“最后的星空战士…”
"The last Starfighter..."

905
01:17:27,012 --> 01:17:28,912
你欠我一个人情，亚里克斯
You owe me one, Alex.

906
01:17:35,254 --> 01:17:36,414
亚里克斯！
Alex!

907
01:17:39,124 --> 01:17:41,459
通讯中断，指挥长
Transmission pulsars have stopped, Commander.

908
01:17:41,460 --> 01:17:43,361
最后的星空战士…
The last Starfighter...

909
01:17:43,362 --> 01:17:45,023
已死亡！
Is dead!

910
01:17:46,131 --> 01:17:48,430
最后的星空战士已死亡！
The last Starfighter is dead!

911
01:17:49,368 --> 01:17:52,103
我们是无可阻挡的了！全速前进！
Nothing can stop us now. Ahead full.

912
01:17:52,104 --> 01:17:54,038
前往赖罗斯！
To Rylos!

913
01:18:14,159 --> 01:18:15,650
指挥舰！
The command ship!

914
01:18:20,466 --> 01:18:22,935
那儿！塔台在最后面
There! The turret at the far end!

915
01:18:24,703 --> 01:18:25,932
我看见了
I see it.

916
01:18:29,108 --> 01:18:30,507
祝你好运，星空战士
Good luck, Starfighter.

917
01:18:31,210 --> 01:18:33,508
谢谢你所做的一切，格里格
Thanks, Grig. For everything.

918
01:18:47,126 --> 01:18:48,991
我爱你，亚里克斯罗根
I love you, Alex Rogan.

919
01:18:50,529 --> 01:18:51,758
六
Six.

920
01:18:53,065 --> 01:18:54,265
显示器，开启
Heads-up display. Check.

921
01:18:54,266 --> 01:18:55,399
五
Five.

922
01:18:55,400 --> 01:18:57,301
激光枪，开启
Lasers. Check.

923
01:18:57,302 --> 01:19:00,004
-四 -粒子枪，开启
Four. Particle beam. Check.

924
01:19:00,005 --> 01:19:01,772
-三 -霹雳弹，开启
Three. Proton bolts. Check.

925
01:19:01,773 --> 01:19:04,308
-二 -座椅控制，开启
Two. Chair control. Check.

926
01:19:04,309 --> 01:19:05,834
一
One.

927
01:19:06,678 --> 01:19:08,203
来吧
Let's do it.

928
01:19:19,124 --> 01:19:20,683
跟踪警报
Tracking alert.

929
01:19:23,795 --> 01:19:26,321
不明飞船。到底是什么？
Unidentified craft. What is it?

930
01:19:31,203 --> 01:19:32,636
等等
Wait.

931
01:19:32,771 --> 01:19:34,239
刚星！
Gunstar!

932
01:19:34,706 --> 01:19:38,939
最后的星空战士不是死了吗？
So, the last Starfighter is dead?

933
01:19:40,078 --> 01:19:43,514
我受够了。抓起来！
This has gone far enough. Seize him!

934
01:19:44,316 --> 01:19:47,985
你们敢！我是赖罗斯的帝王！
How dare you? I am the Emperor of Rylos!

935
01:19:47,986 --> 01:19:50,988
我，只有我，才能指挥这…
I and I alone command this entire op...

936
01:19:50,989 --> 01:19:53,624
放开我！我命令你！
Release me! I command you!

937
01:19:53,625 --> 01:19:56,390
你会付出生命的代价的！
You will pay for this with your lives!

938
01:19:57,462 --> 01:19:59,795
全面开火！
All guns fire!

939
01:20:08,974 --> 01:20:10,874
在那儿，塔台！
There it is, the turret!

940
01:20:11,410 --> 01:20:12,877
亚里克斯，就现在！
Alex, now!

941
01:20:15,013 --> 01:20:16,113
好！
Yeah!

942
01:20:16,114 --> 01:20:17,138
击中了！
Got it!

943
01:20:18,750 --> 01:20:19,984
快，亚里克斯！开火！
Hurry, Alex! Fire!

944
01:20:19,985 --> 01:20:21,475
敌军积聚已经到达了赖罗斯！
The Armada's almost to Rylos!

945
01:20:41,740 --> 01:20:44,175
逃生通道开启
Escape pod activated.

946
01:20:45,844 --> 01:20:47,676
逃生通道开启
Escape pod ignition.

947
01:20:48,614 --> 01:20:50,548
我们的感应器探测不到刚星了
The Gunstar is gone from our sensors.

948
01:20:50,549 --> 01:20:52,346
向指挥部发出警报
Alert wing commanders.

949
01:20:53,018 --> 01:20:55,248
通信塔台已被摧毁
Communication turret is destroyed.

950
01:21:00,392 --> 01:21:03,919
所有的通信雷达系统都瘫痪了，指挥部
All communication radar systems are out, Wing Commander.

951
01:21:04,496 --> 01:21:07,124
成视觉攻击队列
Proceed with a visual attack formation.

952
01:21:10,936 --> 01:21:14,939
维生系统良好。弹药装备量满
Life support good. Ammo packs at peak.

953
01:21:14,940 --> 01:21:16,741
我认为我们要使用死亡霸王花了
I think we've got to use Death Blossom.

954
01:21:16,742 --> 01:21:18,409
记住，死亡霸王花只能在近距离…
Remember, Death Blossom delivers

955
01:21:18,410 --> 01:21:20,640
给目标以重击
only one massive volley at close range.

956
01:21:21,413 --> 01:21:22,913
理论上是这样的
Theoretically.

957
01:21:22,914 --> 01:21:24,382
“理论上”是什么意思？
What do you mean, "Theoretically"?

958
01:21:24,383 --> 01:21:26,550
毕竟，死亡霸王花从来没被测试过
After all, D.B. has never been tested.

959
01:21:26,551 --> 01:21:29,287
它也许会让飞船超负荷，而毁了飞船
It might overload the systems. Blow up the ship.

960
01:21:29,288 --> 01:21:30,454
你还在担心什么，格里格？
What are you worried about, Grig?

961
01:21:30,455 --> 01:21:32,256
理论上，我们已经死了
Theoretically, we should already be dead.

962
01:21:32,257 --> 01:21:33,520
Mmm-hmm.

963
01:21:34,393 --> 01:21:37,123
打开死亡霸王花踏板，开启
Open Death Blossom petals. Switch is on.

964
01:21:51,677 --> 01:21:54,305
没进入射程千万别发动死亡霸王花
Do not trigger D.B. until we're within range.

965
01:21:54,446 --> 01:21:57,148
先用激光攻击，直到我收到信号
Just use your lasers until I give the signal.

966
01:21:57,149 --> 01:21:58,282
记得要…
Remember to lead...

967
01:21:58,283 --> 01:21:59,784
我被星际联盟录取…
I've been recruited by the Star League

968
01:21:59,785 --> 01:22:01,552
防御边境
to defend the Frontier.

969
01:22:01,553 --> 01:22:02,653
准备好了吗？
Now, are you ready?

970
01:22:02,654 --> 01:22:05,282
到时候了。我们开始吧
This is it. Here we go.

971
01:22:05,424 --> 01:22:07,119
冲啊！
Charge!

972
01:22:36,555 --> 01:22:38,045
右面！
On your right!

973
01:22:39,624 --> 01:22:41,092
左面！
Your left!

974
01:22:42,260 --> 01:22:43,626
闪躲！
Evade!

975
01:22:47,466 --> 01:22:49,900
能量储备不足！我们需要时间充电！
Power packs are low! We need time to recharge!

976
01:22:52,204 --> 01:22:54,035
激光能量耗尽
Laser power draining!

977
01:23:02,547 --> 01:23:05,816
格里格，我的武器都用完了。使用霸王花吗？
Grig, my weapons are gone! Should I do it?

978
01:23:05,817 --> 01:23:06,884
慢着，慢着
Easy, easy.

979
01:23:06,885 --> 01:23:08,717
等到他们都在霸王花的射程内
Wait till they're all in Death Blossom range!

980
01:23:18,430 --> 01:23:19,795
发射！
Fire!

981
01:23:53,165 --> 01:23:55,224
我们成功了！
We did it.

982
01:23:55,367 --> 01:23:57,460
是的，我们真的成功了，对吧？
Yes, we actually did, didn't we?

983
01:24:01,239 --> 01:24:02,935
是指挥舰！
The command ship!

984
01:24:03,308 --> 01:24:04,809
指挥长，我们的枪已损坏
Commander, our guns are out.

985
01:24:04,810 --> 01:24:06,544
维修小组正在维修
Damage control is repairing them.

986
01:24:06,545 --> 01:24:10,003
还要什么枪！急速前进！
Forget the guns! Ramming speed!

987
01:24:18,824 --> 01:24:19,957
格里格，我们需要能量！
Grig, we need power!

988
01:24:19,958 --> 01:24:21,790
死亡霸王花用尽了所有的能量
Death Blossom's drained all power.

989
01:24:22,027 --> 01:24:25,725
我正在尽力，我要运行能量激增模式！
I'm working on it. I'm trying to run boost.

990
01:24:29,201 --> 01:24:31,999
我们剩下的只是维生系统的能量
All we have left is life support power!

991
01:24:38,677 --> 01:24:39,974
格里格！
Grig!

992
01:24:46,184 --> 01:24:47,515
好了！
All right!

993
01:24:55,126 --> 01:24:58,858
可以开火了。我们有能量了。开火！开火！
Weapons on! We have them now! Fire. Fire!

994
01:25:21,820 --> 01:25:23,020
估损报告
Damage report!

995
01:25:24,189 --> 01:25:27,758
导航系统瘫痪，转向系统瘫痪
Guidance system out. Auxiliary steering out.

996
01:25:27,759 --> 01:25:29,193
撤退！
Divert!

997
01:25:30,161 --> 01:25:31,595
撤退！
Divert!

998
01:25:31,596 --> 01:25:33,097
转向系统无响应
She won't answer the helm!

999
01:25:33,098 --> 01:25:35,532
我们被锁定在月球的重力轨道上
We're locked into the moon's gravitational pull!

1000
01:25:35,533 --> 01:25:37,058
我们要怎么办？
What do we do?

1001
01:25:40,906 --> 01:25:42,072
只有死路一条
We die.

1002
01:26:03,528 --> 01:26:07,064
代表星际联盟和所有的赖罗斯公民…
On behalf of the Star League and all citizens of Rylos,

1003
01:26:07,065 --> 01:26:10,334
我祝贺你光荣凯旋
I congratulate you on your dazzling victory.

1004
01:26:10,335 --> 01:26:12,002
-谢谢你 -谢谢
Thank you. Thanks.

1005
01:26:12,003 --> 01:26:15,439
但是，你知道，边境已经瓦解…
But as you know, the Frontier is down,

1006
01:26:15,440 --> 01:26:17,975
祖尔也逃跑了。危险依然存在
Xur escaped, and there is still danger.

1007
01:26:17,976 --> 01:26:21,178
所以，我在想，你是不是愿意呆在这儿…
So I was wondering if you wouldn't be willing to stay on,

1008
01:26:21,179 --> 01:26:23,714
重建星际联盟？
and rebuild the Starfighter Legion.

1009
01:26:23,715 --> 01:26:25,240
等等
Wait a minute.

1010
01:26:26,051 --> 01:26:27,718
重建星际联盟？
Rebuild the Legion?

1011
01:26:27,719 --> 01:26:29,084
没错
Yes.

1012
01:26:29,421 --> 01:26:32,823
当然，你也会有一位老朋友来帮忙
Of course, you'd have the help of an old friend.

1013
01:26:33,992 --> 01:26:35,721
老朋友？谁？
An old friend? Who?

1014
01:26:51,910 --> 01:26:54,812
森特利！我以为你死了！
Centauri! I thought you were dead!

1015
01:26:54,813 --> 01:26:58,382
我死了，还错过精彩的战事？哦，不！
Me die and miss all the excitement? Oh, no.

1016
01:26:58,383 --> 01:27:01,018
我只是进入休眠状态好让我的身体自行恢复
I was merely dormant while my body repaired itself.

1017
01:27:01,019 --> 01:27:03,053
我就废话少说了
Now, I won't bore you with details.

1018
01:27:03,054 --> 01:27:05,923
一句话：你在赖罗斯星，我的孩子
Suffice it to say, you're on Rylos, my boy.

1019
01:27:05,924 --> 01:27:07,391
别想着人类了
Stop thinking human.

1020
01:27:07,392 --> 01:27:08,993
这是第一课
That's lesson number one.

1021
01:27:08,994 --> 01:27:12,496
现在，第二课，你在这里远近闻名
Now, lesson number two, you've got a good thing going here.

1022
01:27:12,497 --> 01:27:14,989
保持微笑，别扫兴
Keep smiling. Don't blow it.

1023
01:27:15,333 --> 01:27:18,963
第三课，总是相信森特利
Lesson number three, always trust Centauri.

1024
01:27:23,975 --> 01:27:25,841
亚里克斯，他们多爱你！
Alex, they love you!

1025
01:27:29,914 --> 01:27:32,941
你看，整个赖罗斯星就在你下面
You see, all Rylos is behind you.

1026
01:27:34,319 --> 01:27:35,986
你得留下 ，亚里克斯！
You've got to stay, Alex!

1027
01:27:35,987 --> 01:27:38,022
你会留下的，对吧？
You will stay, won't you?

1028
01:27:38,023 --> 01:27:39,523
当然，他会留下的
Of course, he'll stay.

1029
01:27:40,792 --> 01:27:42,993
这真的很令人欣慰，森特利
That's very reassuring, Centauri.

1030
01:27:42,994 --> 01:27:45,486
格里格，我就把这些事交给你了
Grig, I leave it in your capable hands.

1031
01:27:47,499 --> 01:27:48,966
我留下
I'll stay.

1032
01:28:01,646 --> 01:28:04,741
亚里克斯！亚里克斯！
Alex! Alex!

1033
01:28:18,363 --> 01:28:19,796
你好…
Greetings...

1034
01:28:21,166 --> 01:28:22,900
你好，星空战士
Greetings, Starfighter.

1035
01:28:22,901 --> 01:28:24,368
孩子，你看到亚里克斯了吗？
Bunny, have you seen Alex?

1036
01:28:24,369 --> 01:28:25,769
怎么会呢
Can't say that I have.

1037
01:28:25,770 --> 01:28:29,073
问玛姬吧，她知道他在哪儿
Well, ask Maggie. She knows where he is.

1038
01:28:29,074 --> 01:28:31,075
她原本和他在一起的
She was with him.

1039
01:28:31,076 --> 01:28:32,543
玛姬，亚里克斯呢？
Maggie, where's Alex?

1040
01:28:32,544 --> 01:28:35,212
我的卡车在哪儿？你的男朋友在哪儿？
Yeah, where's my truck? Where's your boyfriend?

1041
01:28:35,213 --> 01:28:37,915
罗根太太，关于亚里克斯，他…
Mrs. Rogan, about Alex, you see, he's...

1042
01:28:41,119 --> 01:28:43,485
